(157, 48, 'service', 'Làm trắng da bằng phương pháp thủy liệu', '{\"icon\":null,\"description\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"brief\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"Li\\u1ec7u ph\\u00e1p Hydra Whitening Facial l\\u00e0m m\\u1edd c\\u00e1c v\\u1ebft t\\u00e0n nhang, n\\u00e1m, \\u0111\\u1ed1m \\u0111en v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m s\\u00e1ng t\\u00f4ng m\\u00e0u da m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 nh\\u1ea5t b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n l\\u00e0m tr\\u1eafng cao c\\u1ea5p, th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n qua c\\u00e1c b\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a Hydrafacial, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u1edf b\\u01b0\\u1edbc cu\\u1ed1i, l\\u00e0m tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp s\\u00e2u h\\u01a1n c\\u1ee7a da\",\"en\":\"The Hydra Whitening Facial lightens freckles, pigmentation, dark spots, and brightens the skin tone using active whitening ingredients delivered through the gentle intensive skin resurfacing steps of the Hydrafacial, to ultimately rejuvenate the deeper layers of the skin.\"},\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"gallery_image\":{\"1691770975282\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/service\\/lifting serum 1.webp\"},\"title\":{\"en\":\"Hydra Whitening Facial\",\"vi\":\"L\\u00e0m tr\\u1eafng da b\\u1eb1ng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p th\\u1ee7y li\\u1ec7u\"}}', '/data/cms-image/service/led deep lifting.jpg', '/data/cms-image/service/tay-te-bao-chet-tai-spa-2.png', 1, 28, 5, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-08-09 02:22:48', '2023-09-06 04:23:03', 'lam-trang-da-bang-phuong-phap-thuy-lieu'),
(158, 48, 'service', 'Trị Mụn bằng phương pháp thủy liệu', '{\"icon\":null,\"description\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"brief\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 v\\u1ec1 m\\u1ee5n hay trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i sau m\\u1ee5n, Hydra Acne Facial Treatment ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 li\\u1ec7u ph\\u00e1p d\\u00e0nh cho b\\u1ea1n. Li\\u1ec7u ph\\u00e1p n\\u00e0y k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n ng\\u1eeba v\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb m\\u1ee5n d\\u00e0nh cho da m\\u1eb7t v\\u00e0 quy tr\\u00ecnh t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da 6 b\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee7a Hydrafacial \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t collagen t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a da nh\\u1eb1m l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n, n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 l\\u1ed7 ch\\u00e2n l\\u00f4ng to, mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u00e0n da m\\u1ecbn m\\u00e0ng, trong tr\\u1ebbo h\\u01a1n.\",\"en\":\"Achieve your clear skin goals and banish acne with the Hydra Acne Facial Treatment. Combining anti-acne facial ingredients and the gentle 6-step skin resurfacing handles of the Hydrafacial to boost skin\\u2019s natural collagen production in lessening fine lines, wrinkles, and open pores, to reveal a smoother, clearer complexion.\"},\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"gallery_image\":{\"1691548216852\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/service\\/1578790f248adc3b7c03ea8a0b919c0b.png\"},\"title\":{\"vi\":\"Tr\\u1ecb M\\u1ee5n b\\u1eb1ng ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph\\u00e1p th\\u1ee7y li\\u1ec7u\",\"en\":\"Hydra Acne Facial\"}}', '/data/cms-image/service/hydra-acne-facial.jpg', '/data/cms-image/service/hydra-acne-facial.jpg', 1, 26, 4, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-08-09 02:30:11', '2023-09-05 04:10:18', 'tri-mun-bang-phuong-phap-thuy-lieu'),
(159, 47, 'service', 'LED nâng cơ chuyên sâu', '{\"icon\":null,\"description\":{\"vi\":\"Demo Text\",\"en\":\"Demo Text\"},\"brief\":{\"vi\":\"Demo Text\",\"en\":\"Demo Text\"},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"Ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng cho l\\u00e0n da c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch khoa h\\u1ecdc v\\u1edbi s\\u1ee9c m\\u1ea1nh c\\u1ee7a tia s\\u00e1ng \\u0110\\u1ecf &amp; H\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i. Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u Zero Gravity Perfectio X \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng cung c\\u1ea5p n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cho da \\u0111\\u1ec3 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch t\\u1ea1o ra c\\u00e1c s\\u1ee3i collagen v\\u00e0 elastin, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng x\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a \\u1edf c\\u1ea3 ba l\\u1edbp bi\\u1ec3u b\\u00ec da.\",\"en\":\"Revitalize your facial skin with the science and power of Red &amp; Infrared Light Perfectio X that gently delivers a precise dosage of energy to the skin to produce collagen fibers and elastin, while gently erasing signs of aging in all three lavers of skin.\"},\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"gallery_image\":{\"1691771325961\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/service\\/relaxing beauty mask 4.jpg\"},\"title\":{\"en\":\"LED Deep Lifting\",\"vi\":\"LED n\\u00e2ng c\\u01a1 chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u\"}}', '/data/cms-image/service/hydra lifting facial.png', '/data/cms-image/service/hydra lifting facial.png', 1, 35, 3, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-08-09 02:31:51', '2023-09-06 02:03:43', 'led-nang-co-chuyen-sau'),
(161, 49, 'service', 'Mặt nạ vàng 24K', '{\"icon\":null,\"description\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"brief\":{\"vi\":null,\"en\":null},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"Ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1 v\\u00e0ng 24K l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t li\\u1ec7u ph\\u00e1p s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n cao c\\u1ea5p, mang l\\u1ea1i m\\u1ed9t l\\u00e0n da kh\\u1ecfe m\\u1ea1nh, tr\\u1ebb trung, tr\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u1ea7y s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng &nbsp;M\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1 v\\u00e0ng 24K gi\\u00fap k\\u00edch th\\u00edch s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o c\\u1ee7a l\\u1edbp bi\\u1ec3u b\\u00ec, t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m s\\u0103n ch\\u1eafc t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o da, kh\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m, t\\u0103ng m\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1ed9 collagen trong da, v\\u00e0 ng\\u0103n ng\\u1eeba s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e2n h\\u1ee7y elastin.\",\"en\":\"Enrich your facial skin with decadent beauty innovations of 24K Gold Mask. It helps stimulate cellular growth of the epidermis, regenerates and firm skin cells, locks in moisture, increases collagen level in the skin, and prevents the breakdown of elastin.\"},\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"gallery_image\":{\"1692153772824\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/service\\/24k-gold-facial-gallery.jpg\",\"1692153784386\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/service\\/24k-gold-facial.jpg\"},\"title\":{\"en\":\"24k Gold Facial\",\"vi\":\"M\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1 v\\u00e0ng 24K\"}}', '/data/cms-image/service/24k-gold-facial-gallery.jpg', NULL, 1, 60, 7, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-08-09 02:36:20', '2023-09-06 03:37:13', 'mat-na-vang-24k'),
(169, 53, 'product', 'LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND', '{\"price\":\"25000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Revive dull, tired and aging skin with LED technology combined with micro-vibration from Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand. This is a non-invasive beauty device that is essential to your skin care routine.\\n\\nSome of the benefits Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand can bring to the skin:\\n\\n- Supports stimulation of collagen production\\n- Detoxifies, helps reduce puffiness\\n- Evens out and brightens skin tone\\n- Helps to tighten facial contours\\n- Increase hydration\\n- Reduces the appearance of blemishes, spots and redness\\n- Restore dull, lifeless skin\",\"vi\":\"H\\u1ed3i sinh l\\u00e0n da x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, m\\u1ec7t m\\u1ecfi v\\u00e0 l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u00e8n LED k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi rung vi m\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1eb9p kh\\u00f4ng x\\u00e2m l\\u1ea5n, r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft cho quy tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.\\n\\nM\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i cho l\\u00e0n da:\\n\\n- H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch s\\u1ea3n sinh collagen\\n- Gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ed9c t\\u1ed1, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft\\n- L\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0 s\\u00e1ng da\\n- Gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m s\\u0103n ch\\u1eafc c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng n\\u00e9t tr\\u00ean khu\\u00f4n m\\u1eb7t\\n- T\\u0103ng hydrat h\\u00f3a\\n- Gi\\u1ea3m s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a nh\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m, \\u0111\\u1ed1m v\\u00e0 m\\u1ea9n \\u0111\\u1ecf\\n- Ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i l\\u00e0n da x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, thi\\u1ebfu s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"PRINCIPLES OF OPERATION\\n\\nLumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand uses photo-biomimicry through red LEDs (Light Emitting Diodes) to gently massage your skin while accelerating your skin\'s natural metabolism for a radiant appearance. and more radiant. LED power, heat energy and vibration work together to improve the appearance of premature aging, addressing issues your skin may be experiencing for fresh, energized skin. and rejuvenation.\\n\\nWavelength and color of emitted light:\\n\\nLight color: red\\nWavelength: 630 - 645 nanometers\\nPhoto biostimulation refers to the use of light to stimulate biological responses by using LEDs to produce light of the wavelength required to achieve the desired results.\\nThe properties of red LEDs can help:\\n\\nSkin rejuvenation\\nMoisturizes the skin\\nSupports stimulation of collagen production\\nImprove skin elasticity\",\"vi\":\"NGUY\\u00caN L\\u00dd HO\\u1ea0T \\u0110\\u1ed8NG\\n\\nLumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00f4 ph\\u1ecfng sinh h\\u1ecdc b\\u1eb1ng \\u1ea3nh th\\u00f4ng qua \\u0111\\u00e8n LED \\u0111\\u1ecf (\\u0110i\\u1ed1t ph\\u00e1t quang) \\u0111\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng massage l\\u00e0n da c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea9y nhanh qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a da \\u0111\\u1ec3 da c\\u00f3 v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i t\\u01b0\\u01a1i s\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 h\\u01a1n. S\\u1ee9c m\\u1ea1nh t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e8n LED, n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nhi\\u1ec7t v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 rung ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u00f9ng nhau \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n s\\u1edbm c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a, gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 m\\u00e0 l\\u00e0n da c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u1eb7p ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 l\\u00e0n da t\\u01b0\\u01a1i m\\u1edbi, tr\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u1ea7y n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a.\\n\\nB\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc c\\u1ee7a \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng ph\\u00e1t ra:\\n\\nM\\u00e0u s\\u00e1ng: \\u0111\\u1ecf\\nB\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f3ng: 630 - 645 nanomet\\nK\\u00edch th\\u00edch sinh h\\u1ecdc \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1ec1 c\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ebfn vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch ph\\u1ea3n \\u1ee9ng sinh h\\u1ecdc b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u00e8n LED \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o ra \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng c\\u00f3 b\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f3ng c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nh\\u01b0 mong mu\\u1ed1n.\\nC\\u00e1c thu\\u1ed9c t\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u00e8n LED \\u0111\\u1ecf c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap:\\n\\nTr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da\\nD\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m cho da\\nH\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch s\\u1ea3n sinh collagen \\nC\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u00e0n h\\u1ed3i c\\u1ee7a da\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"WARNING\\n\\n1. LumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand does not have fireproof function, please keep away from fire or corrosive liquid.\\n\\n2. Do not disassemble or repair this product yourself.\\n\\n3. Please keep out of reach of children.\\n\\n4. This product is not waterproof. Do not wash directly under water.\\n\\n5. Do not press hard to avoid device deformation and damage.\\n\\nSAFETY FIRST\\n\\nDO NOT use this device if:\\n\\n\\u2022 You have bleeding, open wounds, oozing skin (sores, herpes, eczema, psoriasis, sunburn, wounds or rashes).\\n\\n\\u2022 You have infected skin from a burn or cut as this can cause discomfort, irritation or infection.\\n\\n\\u2022 You are being treated with radiation or chemotherapy.\\n\\n\\u2022 You are taking any medications that may cause photosensitivity.\\n\\nGUARANTEE\\n\\nThis LumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand comes with a LIFETIME WARRANTY. If your Opatra LumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand is defective, please return the product along with the repair receipt. The repair will be free provided that you have used the machine according to the instructions for use contained in this manual.\\nThe warranty does NOT cover breakage or damage due to the following:\\n\\nNormal wear and tear of equipment\\nMisuse or failure to follow operating instructions\\/user manual.\\nImproper or unauthorized repair of the device.\",\"vi\":\"C\\u1ea2NH B\\u00c1O\\n\\n1. LumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng ch\\u1ed1ng ch\\u00e1y, vui l\\u00f2ng tr\\u00e1nh xa l\\u1eeda ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng \\u0103n m\\u00f2n.\\n\\n2. Kh\\u00f4ng t\\u1ef1 th\\u00e1o r\\u1eddi ho\\u1eb7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0y.\\n\\n3. Vui l\\u00f2ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 xa t\\u1ea7m tay tr\\u1ebb em.\\n\\n4. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea5m n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. Kh\\u00f4ng r\\u1eeda tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp d\\u01b0\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.\\n\\n5. Kh\\u00f4ng \\u1ea5n m\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00e1nh bi\\u1ebfn d\\u1ea1ng v\\u00e0 h\\u1ecfng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb.\\n\\nAN TO\\u00c0N L\\u00c0 TR\\u00caN H\\u1ebeT\\n\\nKH\\u00d4NG s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb n\\u00e0y n\\u1ebfu:\\n\\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea1n b\\u1ecb ch\\u1ea3y m\\u00e1u, v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1edf, da r\\u1ec9 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc (l\\u1edf lo\\u00e9t, m\\u1ee5n r\\u1ed9p, ch\\u00e0m, v\\u1ea3y n\\u1ebfn, ch\\u00e1y n\\u1eafng, v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ho\\u1eb7c ph\\u00e1t ban).\\n\\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 v\\u00f9ng da b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m tr\\u00f9ng do b\\u1ecb b\\u1ecfng, b\\u1ecb c\\u1eaft v\\u00ec \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu, k\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng ho\\u1eb7c nhi\\u1ec5m tr\\u00f9ng.\\n\\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb b\\u1eb1ng b\\u1ee9c x\\u1ea1 ho\\u1eb7c h\\u00f3a tr\\u1ecb.\\n\\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang d\\u00f9ng b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 lo\\u1ea1i thu\\u1ed1c n\\u00e0o c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m v\\u1edbi \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\n\\nB\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH\\n\\nLumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand n\\u00e0y \\u0111i k\\u00e8m v\\u1edbi B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH TR\\u1eccN \\u0110\\u1edcI. N\\u1ebfu Opatra LumiQuartz Rose Facial Wand c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n b\\u1ecb l\\u1ed7i, vui l\\u00f2ng tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi bi\\u00ean nh\\u1eadn s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa. Vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa s\\u1ebd mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e1y theo c\\u00e1c h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f3 trong s\\u00e1ch h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng n\\u00e0y.\\nB\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh KH\\u00d4NG bao g\\u1ed3m t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng b\\u1ecb v\\u1ee1 ho\\u1eb7c h\\u01b0 h\\u1ecfng do nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u sau \\u0111\\u00e2y:\\n\\nHao m\\u00f2n th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb\\nS\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng sai ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u00f4ng tu\\u00e2n theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh\\/s\\u00e1ch h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\nS\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00fang c\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c tr\\u00e1i ph\\u00e9p.\"},\"information\":{\"en\":\"Revive dull, tired and aging skin with LED technology combined with micro-vibration from Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand. This is a non-invasive beauty device that is essential to your skin care routine.\\n\\nSome of the benefits Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand can bring to the skin:\\n\\n- Supports stimulation of collagen production\\n- Detoxifies, helps reduce puffiness\\n- Evens out and brightens skin tone\\n- Helps to tighten facial contours\\n- Increase hydration\\n- Reduces the appearance of blemishes, spots and redness\\n- Restore dull, lifeless skin\",\"vi\":\"H\\u1ed3i sinh l\\u00e0n da x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, m\\u1ec7t m\\u1ecfi v\\u00e0 l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u00e8n LED k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi rung vi m\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1eb9p kh\\u00f4ng x\\u00e2m l\\u1ea5n, r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft cho quy tr\\u00ecnh ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.\\n\\nM\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch Lumiquartz Rose Facial Wand c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i cho l\\u00e0n da:\\n\\n- H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch s\\u1ea3n sinh collagen\\n- Gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ed9c t\\u1ed1, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft\\n- L\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0 s\\u00e1ng da\\n- Gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m s\\u0103n ch\\u1eafc c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng n\\u00e9t tr\\u00ean khu\\u00f4n m\\u1eb7t\\n- T\\u0103ng hydrat h\\u00f3a\\n- Gi\\u1ea3m s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a nh\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m, \\u0111\\u1ed1m v\\u00e0 m\\u1ea9n \\u0111\\u1ecf\\n- Ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i l\\u00e0n da x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, thi\\u1ebfu s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng\"},\"using\":{\"en\":\"HOW TO USE\\n\\nUse 3-4 times a week for best results, 5-8 minutes on each side.\\n\\n1. For best results, apply 1-2 drops of serum or facial oil to cleansed skin and massage gently to absorb.\\n2. Press the power button for 3 seconds until the LED light turns on automatically, activating vibration and mild heat mode\\n3. To turn off the LED, press the device on\\/off button and the vibration will resume.\\n4. Massage and glide gently in an upward, circular motion for a few minutes over face or areas that need care.\\n5. To switch to different vibration modes, press the Mode button each time for 3 speed types (low - medium - high).\\n6. Press the Mode button for 2 seconds until the indicator light is on to activate the heat mode. To turn off heat mode, press the Mode button again until the indicator light goes off.\\n7. To turn off the device, press the power button.\\n8. After each use, clean the LumiQuartz with a disinfecting wipe or dry cloth and let it dry. Use in combination with Opatra anti-aging creams or serums for enhanced effectiveness.\\n\\nCHARGING THE DEVICE\\n\\n1. When the PIN is low, the LumiQuartz Facial Wand will automatically shut down after the indicator light on the button flashes 10 times.\\n2. While the LumiQuartz Facial Wand is charging, a red light will flash between the Power Control and Mode function buttons.\\n3. When the red indicator light is on continuously, the LumiQuartz Facial Wand is fully charged.\\n\\nPRESERVE\\n\\nAfter use, gently wipe the body and quartz head with a sterile wipe or dry cloth, then dry with a dry cloth. Do not wash directly under water.\\nIf the product is damaged, stop using it.\\nIt is strictly forbidden to disassemble the product yourself. If any problems occur or can\'t be used normally, please stop using and contact customer service.\\nStore in a cool dry place, away from moisture and direct sunlight.\\nDo not put product into liquid.\\nKeep out of reach of CHILDREN.\",\"vi\":\"C\\u00c1CH D\\u00d9NG\\n\\nS\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng 3 \\u2013 4 l\\u1ea7n\\/tu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, m\\u1ed7i b\\u00ean 5 \\u2013 8 ph\\u00fat.\\n\\n1. \\u0110\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, h\\u00e3y nh\\u1ecf 1-2 gi\\u1ecdt serum ho\\u1eb7c d\\u1ea7u d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da m\\u1eb7t l\\u00ean da \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c r\\u1eeda s\\u1ea1ch v\\u00e0 massage nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1ea5m v\\u00e0o da.\\n2. Nh\\u1ea5n n\\u00fat ngu\\u1ed3n trong 3 gi\\u00e2y cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0111\\u00e8n LED t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng b\\u1eadt, k\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 rung v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1eb9\\n3. \\u0110\\u1ec3 t\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u00e8n LED, nh\\u1ea5n n\\u00fat b\\u1eadt\\/t\\u1eaft thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 rung s\\u1ebd ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c.\\n4. M\\u00e1t-xa v\\u00e0 l\\u01b0\\u1edbt nh\\u1eb9 theo chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u00f2n, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng l\\u00ean trong v\\u00e0i ph\\u00fat tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c v\\u00f9ng m\\u1eb7t ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c v\\u00f9ng c\\u1ea7n ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c.\\n5. \\u0110\\u1ec3 chuy\\u1ec3n sang c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 rung kh\\u00e1c nhau, nh\\u1ea5n n\\u00fat Mode m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n cho 3 lo\\u1ea1i t\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 (th\\u1ea5p \\u2013 trung b\\u00ecnh \\u2013 cao).\\n6. Nh\\u1ea5n n\\u00fat Mode trong 2 gi\\u00e2y cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0111\\u00e8n b\\u00e1o s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 k\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 nhi\\u1ec7t. \\u0110\\u1ec3 t\\u1eaft ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 nhi\\u1ec7t, h\\u00e3y nh\\u1ea5n l\\u1ea1i n\\u00fat Mode cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0111\\u00e8n b\\u00e1o t\\u1eaft .\\n7. \\u0110\\u1ec3 t\\u1eaft thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, h\\u00e3y nh\\u1ea5n n\\u00fat ngu\\u1ed3n.\\n8. Sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, h\\u00e3y l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch LumiQuartz b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n lau kh\\u1eed tr\\u00f9ng ho\\u1eb7c v\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u00f4. S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i kem ho\\u1eb7c serum ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u00e2ng cao hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 qu\\u1ea3.\\n\\nS\\u1ea0C THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca\\n\\n1. Khi PIN y\\u1ebfu, LumiQuartz Facial Wand s\\u1ebd t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eaft m\\u00e1y sau khi \\u0111\\u00e8n b\\u00e1o s\\u00e1ng tr\\u00ean n\\u00fat nh\\u1ea5p nh\\u00e1y 10 l\\u1ea7n.\\n2. Khi \\u0111ang s\\u1ea1c LumiQuartz Facial Wand, \\u0111\\u00e8n \\u0111\\u1ecf s\\u1ebd nh\\u1ea5p nh\\u00e1y \\u1edf gi\\u1eefa n\\u00fat ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng Power Control v\\u00e0 Mode.\\n3. Khi \\u0111\\u00e8n b\\u00e1o m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf s\\u00e1ng li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c b\\u00e1o hi\\u1ec7u LumiQuartz Facial Wand \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1ea7y.\\n\\nB\\u1ea2O QU\\u1ea2N\\n\\nSau khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, lau nh\\u1eb9 th\\u00e2n m\\u00e1y v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u00e1 th\\u1ea1ch anh b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n lau ti\\u1ec7t tr\\u00f9ng ho\\u1eb7c v\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4 sau \\u0111\\u00f3 lau kh\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng v\\u1ea3i kh\\u00f4. Kh\\u00f4ng r\\u1eeda tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp d\\u01b0\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.\\nN\\u1ebfu s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m b\\u1ecb h\\u01b0 h\\u1ecfng, h\\u00e3y ng\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\nNghi\\u00eam c\\u1ea5m t\\u1ef1 th\\u00e1o r\\u1eddi s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. N\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3 b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 n\\u00e0o x\\u1ea3y ra ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, vui l\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 v\\u1edbi ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng.\\nB\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n n\\u01a1i kh\\u00f4 m\\u00e1t, tr\\u00e1nh \\u1ea9m \\u01b0\\u1edbt v\\u00e0 \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp.\\nKh\\u00f4ng cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m v\\u00e0o ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng.\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 xa t\\u1ea7m tay tr\\u1ebb em.\"},\"seo_titl\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\",\"vi\":\"THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca L\\u00c0M \\u0110\\u1eb8P LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\"},\"gallery_image\":{\"1693452580115\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/1_LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\\/273564361_2996339520633622_7797252364632083373_n_b2abfbbc92154b02876ec9e37469fd5d_master.webp\",\"1693452580219\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/1_LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\\/274031260_3001790850088489_6016284440989672379_n_b23c6e7a4f5845bcb22645b7843821ba_grande.webp\",\"1693452580572\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/1_LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\\/274060501_3002818099985764_7174155222823536382_n_07f17e2ef59d41998a845c1a35cce6c5_master.webp\",\"1693452580671\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/1_LUMIQUARTZ ROSE FACE WAND\\/278621626_30478