(170, 53, 'product', 'SYNERGY EYE', '{\"price\":\"60000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"OPATRA SYNERGY EYE is a unique, premium skin care device that combines red light therapy with massage and heat therapy to enhance absorption of vitamins and minerals, supporting Reduces wrinkles and brings softness to the skin around the eyes.\",\"vi\":\"OPATRA SYNERGY EYE l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da cao c\\u1ea5p, \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi m\\u00e1t-xa v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec7t tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ea5p thu c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c vitamin v\\u00e0 kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m c\\u00e1c n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 m\\u1ec1m m\\u1ecbn cho v\\u00f9ng da quanh m\\u1eaft.\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"RED LED LIGHT stimulates cells to produce collagen, which can help the skin regain its youthful appearance. Combined with the use of OPATRA\'s anti-aging cream or serum, red light helps the product penetrate deeper into the skin layers while assisting in improving blood circulation, reducing wrinkles and re-linking the skin.\\n\\nMASSAGE and HEAT modes gently stimulate and relax the facial muscles, and thus, stimulate collagen production and increase skin elasticity. It also helps reduce dark spots, brighten skin, improve blood flow and skin elasticity.\\n\\nFor best results, use Synergy Eye in conjunction with Opatra\'s comprehensive line of anti-aging skin care products.\",\"vi\":\"\\u0110\\u00c8N LED M\\u00c0U \\u0110\\u1ece k\\u00edch th\\u00edch c\\u00e1c t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t collagen, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap cho l\\u00e0n da l\\u1ea5y l\\u1ea1i v\\u1ebb t\\u01b0\\u01a1i tr\\u1ebb. K\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kem ho\\u1eb7c serum ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a OPATRA, \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ecf s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea5m s\\u00e2u h\\u01a1n v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp da \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n tu\\u1ea7n ho\\u00e0n m\\u00e1u, gi\\u1ea3m n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft da.\\n\\nCh\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 M\\u00c1T-XA v\\u00e0 L\\u00c0M N\\u00d3NG k\\u00edch th\\u00edch nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0 gi\\u00e3n c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 m\\u1eb7t, v\\u00e0 nh\\u1edd \\u0111\\u00f3, k\\u00edch th\\u00edch s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t collagen v\\u00e0 t\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u00e0n h\\u1ed3i cho da. N\\u00f3 c\\u00f2n gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m c\\u00e1c v\\u1ebft th\\u00e2m n\\u00e1m, l\\u00e0m s\\u00e1ng da, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n d\\u00f2ng m\\u00e1u v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u00e0n h\\u1ed3i c\\u1ee7a da.\\n\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng Synergy Eye k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb Opatra.\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"SAFETY FIRST\\n\\nDO NOT use this device if:\\n\\nYou are pregnant or breastfeeding\\nYou have light-onset epilepsy.\\nYou are suffering from lupus erythematosus, photosensitizing eczema, or albinism.\\nYou are bleeding, have an open or watery wound, such as a sore, herpes simplex, eczema, psoriasis, sunburn, wound or skin rash.\\nYou are taking medications that can cause increased photosensitivity.\\nYou have a medical condition that makes your skin especially sensitive to light, such as systemic lupus erythematosus, porphyria, photosynthetic rash, and photo urticaria.\\nYou have infected, burned, or cut skin, as these conditions can cause discomfort or irritation.\\nYou are having radiation or chemotherapy.\\nDo you have a history of heart disease or other medical conditions?\\n\\nWARNINGS AND CAUTION\\n\\nThe basic safety rules listed below should be observed when using the device.\\nThis is not a comprehensive list but will help ensure your safety and help you maintain the maximum life of your product.\\n\\u2022 Keep out of reach of CHILDREN.\\n\\u2022 For use only in persons over 18 years of age.\\n\\u2022 Store the device away from direct sunlight and moisture.\\n\\u2022 Do not immerse the device in water.\\n\\u2022 Do not disassemble the device arbitrarily.\\n\\u2022 For external use only.\\n\\u2022 Avoid direct contact with eyes.\\n\\u2022 If irritation occurs, discontinue use immediately and seek medical attention.\\n\\nGUARANTEE\\n\\nThis product has a LIFETIME WARRANTY. If the Synergy Opatra device has a defect within the first 1 year of purchase, please return the product with the sales receipt, and we will repair the device for you.\\nThis repair will be free as long as you have used the Opatra Synergy Eye device in accordance with the user manual.\\n\\nWarranty will NOT cover breakage or damage caused by:\\n\\nNormal wear and tear of equipment\\nImproper use or treatment \\u2013 failure to follow operating instructions\\/instructions.\\nSelf-repair or improper repair of the device.\",\"vi\":\"AN TO\\u00c0N L\\u00c0 TR\\u00caN H\\u1ebeT\\n\\nKH\\u00d4NG s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb n\\u00e0y n\\u1ebfu:\\n\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 thai ho\\u1eb7c cho con b\\u00fa\\nB\\u1ea1n m\\u1eafc ch\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng kinh kh\\u1edfi ph\\u00e1t do \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang b\\u1ecb Lupus ban \\u0111\\u1ecf, ch\\u00e0m nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ea1ch t\\u1ea1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang b\\u1ecb ch\\u1ea3y m\\u00e1u, c\\u00f3 v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1edf ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u1ea3y n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, nh\\u01b0 v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng g\\u00e2y \\u0111au, herpes simplex, ch\\u00e0m, v\\u1ea3y n\\u1ebfn, ch\\u00e1y n\\u1eafng, v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ho\\u1eb7c ban da.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang d\\u00f9ng thu\\u1ed1c c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y t\\u0103ng nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang m\\u1eafc b\\u1ec7nh l\\u00fd khi\\u1ebfn cho da \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m v\\u1edbi \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, nh\\u01b0 lupus ban \\u0111\\u1ecf h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng, r\\u1ed1i lo\\u1ea1n chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u00f3a porphyrin, ph\\u00e1t ban \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng do \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0y \\u0111ay \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 da b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m tr\\u00f9ng, b\\u1ecb b\\u1ecfng, b\\u1ecb c\\u1eaft, do nh\\u1eefng t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu ho\\u1eb7c k\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang x\\u1ea1 tr\\u1ecb ho\\u1eb7c h\\u00f3a tr\\u1ecb.\\nB\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 ti\\u1ec1n s\\u1eed b\\u1ec7nh tim ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c b\\u1ec7nh l\\u00fd kh\\u00e1c\\n\\nC\\u1ea2NH B\\u00c1O V\\u00c0 TH\\u1eacN TR\\u1eccNG\\n\\nC\\u1ea7n tu\\u00e2n th\\u1ee7 c\\u00e1c quy t\\u1eafc an to\\u00e0n c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c li\\u1ec7t k\\u00ea b\\u00ean d\\u01b0\\u1edbi khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb.\\n\\u0110\\u00e2y kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t danh s\\u00e1ch to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n nh\\u01b0ng s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ef1 an to\\u00e0n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n v\\u00e0 gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n duy tr\\u00ec tu\\u1ed5i th\\u1ecd t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a c\\u1ee7a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. \\n\\u2022 \\u0110\\u1ec3 xa t\\u1ea7m tay tr\\u1ebb em.\\n\\u2022 Ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u1edf ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u00ean 18 tu\\u1ed5i. \\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb tr\\u00e1nh \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m. \\n\\u2022 Kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u00fang thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.\\n\\u2022 Kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ef1 \\u00fd th\\u00e1o r\\u1eddi thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb.\\n\\u2022 Ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngo\\u00e0i da.\\n\\u2022 Tr\\u00e1nh ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi m\\u1eaft.\\n\\u2022 N\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3 k\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng, h\\u00e3y ng\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 th\\u0103m kh\\u00e1m y t\\u1ebf. \\n\\nB\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH\\n\\nS\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH TR\\u1eccN \\u0110\\u1edcI. N\\u1ebfu thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Opatra c\\u00f3 l\\u1ed7i trong v\\u00f2ng 1 n\\u0103m \\u0111\\u1ea7u sau khi mua, vui l\\u00f2ng g\\u1eedi tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u01a1n b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb cho b\\u1ea1n. \\nVi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed mi\\u1ec5n l\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Eye c\\u1ee7a Opatra theo \\u0111\\u00fang h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n\\nB\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh s\\u1ebd KH\\u00d4NG bao g\\u1ed3m tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p l\\u00e0m v\\u1ee1 ho\\u1eb7c l\\u00e0m h\\u1ecfng do: \\n\\nHao m\\u00f2n th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb \\nS\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng sai c\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb sai c\\u00e1ch \\u2013 kh\\u00f4ng tu\\u00e2n th\\u1ee7 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh\\/h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. \\nT\\u1ef1 \\u00fd s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa ho\\u1eb7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00fang c\\u00e1ch.\"},\"information\":{\"en\":\"OPATRA SYNERGY EYE is a unique, premium skin care device that combines red light therapy with massage and heat therapy to enhance absorption of vitamins and minerals, supporting Reduces wrinkles and brings softness to the skin around the eyes.\",\"vi\":\"OPATRA SYNERGY EYE l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da cao c\\u1ea5p, \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi m\\u00e1t-xa v\\u00e0 nhi\\u1ec7t tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ea5p thu c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c vitamin v\\u00e0 kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m c\\u00e1c n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 m\\u1ec1m m\\u1ecbn cho v\\u00f9ng da quanh m\\u1eaft.\"},\"using\":{\"en\":\"USER MANUAL\\n\\n1. Clean skin before using SYNERGY EYE. Remove makeup or remove impurities.\\n2. Thoroughly dry the treatment area.\\n3. We recommend applying OPATRA EYE SERUM to the treatment area. Apply to the area around the eyes \\u2013 under the eyes and outer corners. However, best results can also be obtained by combining SYNERGY EYE with Opatra anti-aging eye care products when using the device.\\n4. Lift the SYNERGY device from the base and turn it on by pressing the control button for 2 seconds (round button). The yellow LED indicator on the device body will light up along with the low wavelength infrared light mode.\\n5. Start your session \\u2013 ready to use.\\n6. Place the surface of the treatment head (metal part) on the skin, the red and infrared LED light mode, heating mode and vibration mode (small sound) will be automatically activated.\\n7. Gently press and slowly move the SYNERGY DEVICE in slow motion from the inner corner to the outer corner of the eye.\\n8. Massage the treatment area for about 4-5 minutes on each side.\\n9. Apply OPATRA EYE CREAM and continue massaging for another 4-5 minutes or until the eye product is completely absorbed.\\n10. When you have completed your treatment session, turn OFF the device by pressing and holding the control button for 2 seconds. The indicator light will turn off.\\n11. It is recommended that after each treatment, you apply a small amount of cream to the treatment area.\\n12. After each use, clean the stainless steel treatment head with a damp cloth (not wet wipes) or with sterile cotton. Dry thoroughly with a soft dry cloth or paper towel and place back on the base.\\n\\n*Immediately after treatment, the treated area may be red. Within 1 hour, the skin will return to normal.\\n\\nEQUIPMENT CLEANING\\n\\nAfter each use, clean the stainless steel treatment head of the SYNERGY OPATRA device with a damp cloth (not wet wipes) or with sterile cotton. Dry with a soft dry cloth or paper towel and place the device back in the base.\\nAlways clean the device after each use.\\nAvoid using detergents or cleaning chemicals to clean the device.\\n\\nSTORAGE DEVICES\\n\\nIf you plan to not use Synergy Eye for an extended period of time, turn OFF the charging device and store its components in a clean, dry place.\\nStore the Synergy Eye device away from water and liquids.\\nStore the Synergy Eye device away from sunlight.\\n\\nCHARGING THE DEVICE\\n\\nRechargeable Synergy Eye device\\nThe Synergy Eye device should be fully charged before use and usage time will reach up to 2 hours when fully charged.\\nIf you find your Synergy Eye device is not charged, charge it for 2 hours before using it.\\nDo not charge for more than 2 hours to avoid overheating the device.\\nYou cannot use the Synergy Eye device while in charging mode.\\nRelated products\",\"vi\":\"H\\u01af\\u1edaNG D\\u1eaaN S\\u1eec D\\u1ee4NG\\n\\n1. L\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch da tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng SYNERGY EYE. T\\u1ea9y trang ho\\u1eb7c lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t b\\u1ea9n.\\n2. Lau th\\u1eadt kh\\u00f4 c\\u1ea7n v\\u00f9ng tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u.\\n3. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i khuy\\u1ebfn ngh\\u1ecb b\\u00f4i SERUM M\\u1eaeT C\\u1ee6A OPATRA l\\u00ean v\\u00f9ng tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u. B\\u00f4i l\\u00ean v\\u00f9ng quanh m\\u1eaft \\u2013 d\\u01b0\\u1edbi m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 g\\u00f3c ngo\\u00e0i. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p SYNERGY EYE v\\u1edbi d\\u00f9ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m kem ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da m\\u1eaft, ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb. \\n4. Nh\\u1ea5c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY ra kh\\u1ecfi \\u0111\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 b\\u1eadt thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u1ea5n n\\u00fat \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n trong 2 gi\\u00e2y (n\\u00fat tr\\u00f2n). \\u0110\\u00e8n LED ch\\u1ec9 m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng tr\\u00ean th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd s\\u00e1ng l\\u00ean c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f3ng th\\u1ea5p. \\n5. B\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u phi\\u00ean \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb \\u2013 s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n6. \\u0110\\u1eb7t b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u (ph\\u1ea7n b\\u1eb1ng kim lo\\u1ea1i) l\\u00ean da, ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u00e8n LED m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 rung (\\u00e2m thanh nh\\u1ecf) s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng k\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t. \\n7. \\u1ea4n nh\\u1eb9 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb di chuy\\u1ec3n THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca SYNERGY theo chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u1eadm t\\u1eeb g\\u00f3c trong ra ph\\u00eda b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i c\\u1ee7a m\\u1eaft. \\n8. M\\u00e1t-xa v\\u00f9ng tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u kho\\u1ea3ng 4-5 ph\\u00fat \\u1edf m\\u1ed7i b\\u00ean.\\n9. B\\u00f4i KEM D\\u01af\\u1ee0NG M\\u1eaeT OPATRA v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c m\\u00e1t-xa th\\u00eam 4-5 ph\\u00fat ho\\u1eb7c cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng m\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u1ea5m ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n. \\n10. Khi \\u0111\\u00e3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh phi\\u00ean tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u, T\\u1eaeT thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef n\\u00fat \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n trong 2 gi\\u00e2y. \\u0110\\u00e8n ch\\u1ec9 th\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd t\\u1eaft. \\n11. Khuy\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1o sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u, b\\u1ea1n h\\u00e3y b\\u00f4i m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ecf kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng l\\u00ean v\\u00f9ng tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u. \\n12. Sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, v\\u1ec7 sinh \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng th\\u00e9p kh\\u00f4ng g\\u1ec9 b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n \\u1ea9m (kh\\u00f4ng d\\u00f9ng kh\\u0103n \\u01b0\\u1edbt) ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1eb1ng b\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 tr\\u00f9ng. Lau th\\u1eadt kh\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n kh\\u00f4 m\\u1ec1m ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u0103n gi\\u1ea5y v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7t l\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ebf.\\n\\n*Ngay sau khi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb, v\\u00f9ng da \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ecf. Trong v\\u00f2ng 1 gi\\u1edd, da s\\u1ebd tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.\\n\\nV\\u1ec6 SINH THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca\\n\\nSau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, v\\u1ec7 sinh \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng th\\u00e9p kh\\u00f4ng g\\u1ec9 c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY OPATRA b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n \\u1ea9m (kh\\u00f4ng d\\u00f9ng kh\\u0103n \\u01b0\\u1edbt) ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1eb1ng b\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 khu\\u1ea9n. Lau kh\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n kh\\u00f4 m\\u1ec1m ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u0103n gi\\u1ea5y v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ebf.\\nLu\\u00f4n lu\\u00f4n v\\u1ec7 sinh thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\nTr\\u00e1nh s\\u1eed