(171, 53, 'product', 'SYNERGY NECK', '{\"price\":\"80000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"The SYNERGY NECK device features rejuvenation technology with simple use, premium design and support against sagging skin on and near the neck.\\n\\nThe combination of the triple energy system of light, heat and kinetic massage combined with anti-aging skin care will help increase collagen, tighten the skin, and rejuvenate the skin in the neck and near the neck area.\\n\\nBenefit from our premium skin care products\\/serums along with advanced technology suitable for use on other skin areas to improve dark spots and uneven skin tone.\\n\\nFor best results, OPATRA Synergy Neck should be used in conjunction with Opatra\'s comprehensive line of anti-aging skin care products.\",\"vi\":\"Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY NECK c\\u00f3 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf cao c\\u1ea5p v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea3y x\\u1ec7 da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng da c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nS\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ed9 ba n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, nhi\\u1ec7t v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1t-xa \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng collagen, l\\u00e0m c\\u0103ng da, tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nL\\u1ee3i \\u00edch t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da\\/serum cao c\\u1ea5p c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng da kh\\u00e1c nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u00e2m n\\u00e1m v\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc da kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u. \\n\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng OPATRA Synergy Neck v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a Opatra. \"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"The SYNERGY NECK device features rejuvenation technology with simple use, premium design and support against sagging skin on and near the neck.\\n\\nThe combination of the triple energy system of light, heat and kinetic massage combined with anti-aging skin care will help increase collagen, tighten the skin, and rejuvenate the skin in the neck and near the neck area.\\n\\nBenefit from our premium skin care products\\/serums along with advanced technology suitable for use on other skin areas to improve dark spots and uneven skin tone.\\n\\nFor best results, OPATRA Synergy Neck should be used in conjunction with Opatra\'s comprehensive line of anti-aging skin care products.\\n\\nLIGHT TECHNOLOGY\\n\\nRed LED light \\u2013 Anti-aging\\nThe red LED light stimulates collagen-producing cells, which in turn can help rejuvenate the skin. When using anti-aging cream or serum, red light helps the product penetrate deep into the skin layers while improving blood circulation, reducing wrinkles and regenerating cells.\\n\\nBlue LED light \\u2013 Treat dark spots\\nThe blue LED light attacks the acne-causing bacteria located below the surface of the skin. Light supports the growth of oxygen radicals, killing harmful bacteria on the skin.\\n\\nGreen LED light \\u2013 Evens out skin tone\\nGreen LED light helps reduce pigmented areas and skin redness, helps cool the skin, evens out skin tone and improves epidermal hyperpigmentation.\",\"vi\":\"Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY NECK c\\u00f3 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf cao c\\u1ea5p v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea3y x\\u1ec7 da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng da c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nS\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ed9 ba n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, nhi\\u1ec7t v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1t-xa \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng collagen, l\\u00e0m c\\u0103ng da, tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nL\\u1ee3i \\u00edch t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da\\/serum cao c\\u1ea5p c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng da kh\\u00e1c nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u00e2m n\\u00e1m v\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc da kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u. \\n\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng OPATRA Synergy Neck v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a Opatra. \\n\\nC\\u00d4NG NGH\\u1ec6 \\u00c1NH S\\u00c1NG\\n\\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf \\u2013 Ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a \\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf k\\u00edch th\\u00edch c\\u00e1c t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t collagen, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 gi\\u00fap tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da. V\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ho\\u1eb7c serum ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a, \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf gi\\u00fap cho s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea5m s\\u00e2u v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp da \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n tu\\u1ea7n ho\\u00e0n m\\u00e1u, gi\\u1ea3m n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 t\\u00e1i t\\u1ea1o t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o. \\n\\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u xanh d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u2013 Tr\\u1ecb th\\u00e2m n\\u00e1m\\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u xanh d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ea5n c\\u00f4ng vi khu\\u1ea9n g\\u00e2y m\\u1ee5n n\\u1eb1m \\u1edf d\\u01b0\\u1edbi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da. \\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c g\\u1ed1c oxy, di\\u1ec7t c\\u00e1c lo\\u00e0i vi khu\\u1ea9n g\\u00e2y h\\u1ea1i tr\\u00ean da.\\n\\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u xanh l\\u00e1\\u2013 L\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u da\\n\\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED m\\u00e0u xanh l\\u00e1 gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m c\\u00e1c v\\u00f9ng s\\u1eafc t\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ecf da, gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m m\\u00e1t da, l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u da v\\u00e0 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng t\\u0103ng s\\u1eafc t\\u1ed1 \\u1edf bi\\u1ec3u b\\u00ec.\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"SAFETY FIRST\\n\\nDO NOT use this device if:\\n\\nYou are pregnant or breastfeeding\\nYou have light-onset epilepsy.\\nYou are suffering from lupus erythematosus, photosensitizing eczema, or albinism.\\nYou are bleeding, have an open or watery wound, such as a sore, herpes simplex, eczema, psoriasis, sunburn, wound or skin rash.\\nYou are taking medications that can cause increased photosensitivity.\\nYou have a medical condition that makes your skin especially sensitive to light, such as systemic lupus erythematosus, porphyria, photosynthetic rash, and photo urticaria.\\nYou have infected, burned, or cut skin, as these conditions can cause discomfort or irritation.\\nYou are having radiation or chemotherapy.\\nDo you have a history of heart disease or other medical conditions?\\n\\nWARNINGS AND CAUTION\\n\\nThe basic safety rules listed below should be observed when using the device.\\nThis is not a comprehensive list but will help ensure your safety and help you maintain the maximum life of your product.\\n\\nKeep out of reach of CHILDREN.\\nFor use only in persons over 18 years of age.\\nStore the device away from direct sunlight and moisture.\\nDo not immerse the device in water.\\nDo not disassemble the device by yourself.\\nFor external use only.\\nAvoid direct contact with eyes.\\nIf irritation occurs, discontinue use immediately and seek medical attention.\\n\\nGUARANTEE\\n\\nThis product comes with a LIFETIME WARRANTY. If the Synergy Opatra device has a defect within the first 1 year of purchase, please return the product with the sales receipt, and we will repair the device for you.\\nThis repair will be free of charge as long as you have used your Synergy Opatra device according to the instructions.\\nWarranty will NOT cover breakage or damage caused by:\\n\\nNormal wear and tear of equipment\\nImproper use or treatment \\u2013 failure to follow operating instructions\\/instructions.\\nSelf-repair or improper repair of the device.\",\"vi\":\"AN TO\\u00c0N L\\u00c0 TR\\u00caN H\\u1ebeT\\n\\nKH\\u00d4NG s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb n\\u00e0y n\\u1ebfu:\\n\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 thai ho\\u1eb7c cho con b\\u00fa\\nB\\u1ea1n m\\u1eafc ch\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng kinh kh\\u1edfi ph\\u00e1t do \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang b\\u1ecb Lupus ban \\u0111\\u1ecf, ch\\u00e0m nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ea1ch t\\u1ea1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang b\\u1ecb ch\\u1ea3y m\\u00e1u, c\\u00f3 v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1edf ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u1ea3y n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, nh\\u01b0 v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng g\\u00e2y \\u0111au, herpes simplex, ch\\u00e0m, v\\u1ea3y n\\u1ebfn, ch\\u00e1y n\\u1eafng, v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ho\\u1eb7c ban da.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang d\\u00f9ng thu\\u1ed1c c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y t\\u0103ng nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang m\\u1eafc b\\u1ec7nh l\\u00fd khi\\u1ebfn cho da \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m v\\u1edbi \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, nh\\u01b0 lupus ban \\u0111\\u1ecf h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng, r\\u1ed1i lo\\u1ea1n chuy\\u1ec3n h\\u00f3a porphyrin, ph\\u00e1t ban \\u0111a d\\u1ea1ng do \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e0y \\u0111ay \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 da b\\u1ecb nhi\\u1ec5m tr\\u00f9ng, b\\u1ecb b\\u1ecfng, b\\u1ecb c\\u1eaft, do nh\\u1eefng t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 g\\u00e2y kh\\u00f3 ch\\u1ecbu ho\\u1eb7c k\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng.\\nB\\u1ea1n \\u0111ang x\\u1ea1 tr\\u1ecb ho\\u1eb7c h\\u00f3a tr\\u1ecb.\\nB\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 ti\\u1ec1n s\\u1eed b\\u1ec7nh tim ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c b\\u1ec7nh l\\u00fd kh\\u00e1c\\n\\nC\\u1ea2NH B\\u00c1O V\\u00c0 TH\\u1eacN TR\\u1eccNG\\n\\nC\\u1ea7n tu\\u00e2n th\\u1ee7 c\\u00e1c quy t\\u1eafc an to\\u00e0n c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c li\\u1ec7t k\\u00ea b\\u00ean d\\u01b0\\u1edbi khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb.\\n\\u0110\\u00e2y kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t danh s\\u00e1ch to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n nh\\u01b0ng s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o s\\u1ef1 an to\\u00e0n c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n v\\u00e0 gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n duy tr\\u00ec tu\\u1ed5i th\\u1ecd t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a c\\u1ee7a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m. \\n\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 xa t\\u1ea7m tay tr\\u1ebb em.\\nCh\\u1ec9 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u1edf ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u00ean 18 tu\\u1ed5i. \\nB\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb tr\\u00e1nh \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m. \\nKh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u00fang thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.\\nKh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ef1 \\u00fd th\\u00e1o r\\u1eddi thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb.\\nCh\\u1ec9 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngo\\u00e0i da.\\nTr\\u00e1nh ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi m\\u1eaft.\\nN\\u1ebfu c\\u00f3 k\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng, h\\u00e3y ng\\u1eebng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 th\\u0103m kh\\u00e1m y t\\u1ebf. \\n\\nB\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH\\n\\nS\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 k\\u00e8m theo B\\u1ea2O H\\u00c0NH TR\\u1eccN \\u0110\\u1edcI. N\\u1ebfu thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Opatra c\\u00f3 l\\u1ed7i trong v\\u00f2ng 1 n\\u0103m \\u0111\\u1ea7u sau khi mua, vui l\\u00f2ng g\\u1eedi tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u01a1n b\\u00e1n h\\u00e0ng, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i s\\u1ebd s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb cho b\\u1ea1n. \\nVi\\u1ec7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed mi\\u1ec5n l\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u00e3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Opatra theo \\u0111\\u00fang h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn.\\nB\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh s\\u1ebd KH\\u00d4NG bao g\\u1ed3m tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p l\\u00e0m v\\u1ee1 ho\\u1eb7c l\\u00e0m h\\u1ecfng do: \\n\\nHao m\\u00f2n th\\u00f4ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb \\nS\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng sai c\\u00e1ch ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb sai c\\u00e1ch \\u2013 kh\\u00f4ng tu\\u00e2n th\\u1ee7 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn v\\u1eadn h\\u00e0nh\\/h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. \\nT\\u1ef1 \\u00fd s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa ho\\u1eb7c s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00fang c\\u00e1ch.\"},\"information\":{\"en\":\"The SYNERGY NECK device features rejuvenation technology with simple use, premium design and support against sagging skin on and near the neck.\\n\\nThe combination of the triple energy system of light, heat and kinetic massage combined with anti-aging skin care will help increase collagen, tighten the skin, and rejuvenate the skin in the neck and near the neck area.\\n\\nBenefit from our premium skin care products\\/serums along with advanced technology suitable for use on other skin areas to improve dark spots and uneven skin tone.\\n\\nFor best results, OPATRA Synergy Neck should be used in conjunction with Opatra\'s comprehensive line of anti-aging skin care products.\",\"vi\":\"Thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY NECK c\\u00f3 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf cao c\\u1ea5p v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea3y x\\u1ec7 da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng da c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nS\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ed9 ba n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng, nhi\\u1ec7t v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1t-xa \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng collagen, l\\u00e0m c\\u0103ng da, tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng c\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 g\\u1ea7n c\\u1ed5. \\n\\nL\\u1ee3i \\u00edch t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da\\/serum cao c\\u1ea5p c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng da kh\\u00e1c nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng th\\u00e2m n\\u00e1m v\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc da kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u. \\n\\n\\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng OPATRA Synergy Neck v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a Opatra. \"},\"using\":{\"en\":\"USER MANUAL\\n\\n1. Clean skin before using SYNERGY NECK.\\n2. Dry skin.\\n3. We recommend applying Opatra anti-aging serum\\/cream on the treatment area. Apply a thin layer of cream or serum for optimal effect. However, for best results, the SYNERGY NECK device should be used in combination with Opatra\'s anti-aging skin care product line.\\n4. Remove the protective cover from the device.\\n5. Lift the Synergy device off the base and turn it on by pressing the control button (round button) for 2 seconds. The yellow LED on the body of the device will light up with low wavelength infrared mode.\\n6. Click the round button at the top and choose the color of the LED light you want.\\n7. Start of session \\u2013 ready to use.\\n8. Place the surface of the CURVE tip on the skin, the selected infrared and LED light modes as well as heating and vibration (low sound) modes will automatically activate.\\n9. Select the desired mode (RED - BLUE - GREEN)\\n10. To switch from RED LED LIGHT to GREEN LED LIGHT to BLUE LED LIGHT between treatment sessions - press and hold the top control button (1 second).\\n11. Gently press and slowly move the Synergy Neck device in an upward direction.\\n12. Treatment for about 5-7 minutes on each side.\\n13. When the treatment session is completed, turn the device OFF by pressing and holding the control button (button below) for 2 seconds. The indicator light will turn off.\\n14. It is recommended to apply a small amount of moisturizer to the treatment area after each treatment session.\\n15. After each use, clean the stainless steel treatment head of the Opatra Synergy Neck device with an OPATRA cleaning cloth or with sterile cotton. Dry with a towel or paper towel and place back on the base.\\n*Immediately after treatment, the treated area may be red. Within 1 hour, the skin will return to normal.\\n\\nEQUIPMENT CLEANING\\n\\n\\u2022 After each use, clean the stainless steel treatment head of the Synergy Neck Opatra device with a damp cloth (do not use a wet cloth) or with sterile cotton. Dry with a soft dry cloth or paper towel and place the device back in the base.\\n\\u2022 Always clean the device after each use.\\n\\u2022 Always close the protective cap after each use.\\n\\u2022 Avoid using detergents or cleaning chemicals to clean the device.\\n\\nSTORAGE DEVICES\\n\\n\\u2022 If you will not use Synergy Neck for an extended period of time, turn OFF the charging device and store its components in a clean, dry place..\\n\\u2022 Store the Synergy Neck device away from water and liquids.\\n\\u2022 Store the Synergy Neck device out of direct sunlight.\\nOPATRA\'s SYNERGY NECK IS NOT WATERPROOF\\n\\u2022 DO NOT allow water or other liquids to enter the device.\\n\\u2022 DO NOT touch Synergy Neck with wet hands.\\n\\u2022 DO NOT put the device in or get water or other liquids into it.\\n\\u2022 DO NOT wash the Synergy Neck device in water or other liquids.\\n\\nCHARGING THE DEVICE\\n\\n\\u2022 Synergy Neck should be fully charged before use and usage time will reach up to 2 hours when fully charged.\\n\\u2022 If you find that your Synergy Neck device is not charged, charge it for 2 hours before using it.\\n\\u2022 Do not charge for more than 2 hours to avoid overheating the device.\\n\\u2022 You cannot use the Synergy Neck device while it is in charging mode.\",\"vi\":\"H\\u01af\\u1edaNG D\\u1eaaN S\\u1eec D\\u1ee4NG\\n\\n1. L\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch da tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng SYNERGY NECK.\\n2. L\\u00e0m kh\\u00f4 da.\\n3. Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i khuy\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1o n\\u00ean b\\u00f4i serum\\/kem ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra tr\\u00ean v\\u00f9ng tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u. B\\u00f4i m\\u1ed9t l\\u1edbp kem ho\\u1eb7c serum m\\u1ecfng \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ed1i \\u01b0u hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb SYNERGY NECK v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra.\\n4. Th\\u00e1o v\\u1ecf b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 ra kh\\u1ecfi thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb. \\n5. Nh\\u1ea5c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy ra kh\\u1ecfi \\u0111\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 b\\u1eadt thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u00ean b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u1ea5n n\\u00fat \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n (n\\u00fat tr\\u00f2n) trong 2 gi\\u00e2y. \\u0110\\u00e8n LED m\\u00e0u v\\u00e0ng tr\\u00ean th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd s\\u00e1ng l\\u00ean c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i b\\u01b0\\u1edbc s\\u00f3ng th\\u1ea5p. \\n6. \\u1ea4n v\\u00e0o n\\u00fat tr\\u00f2n \\u1edf ph\\u00eda tr\\u00ean v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ecdn m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc c\\u1ee7a \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u00e8n LED m\\u00e0 b\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n. \\n7. B\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u phi\\u00ean tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u \\u2013 s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n8. \\u0110\\u1eb7t b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea7u H\\u00ccNH CONG l\\u00ean da, ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u00e8n LED \\u0111\\u00e3 ch\\u1ecdn c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 l\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 rung (\\u00e2m thanh nh\\u1ecf) s\\u1ebd t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng k\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t. \\n9. L\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 theo \\u00fd th\\u00edch (M\\u00c0U \\u0110\\u1ece - M\\u00c0U XANH D\\u01af\\u01a0NG \\u2013 M\\u00c0U XANH L\\u00c1) \\n10. \\u0110\\u1ec3 chuy\\u1ec3n t\\u1eeb \\u00c1NH S\\u00c1NG \\u0110\\u00c8N LED M\\u00c0U \\u0110\\u1ece sang \\u0110\\u00c8N LED \\u00c1NH S\\u00c1NG M\\u00c0U XANH L\\u00c1 sang \\u00c1NH S\\u00c1NG \\u0110\\u00c8N LED M\\u00c0U XANH D\\u01af\\u01a0NG gi\\u1eefa c\\u00e1c phi\\u00ean tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u - \\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef n\\u00fat \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n \\u1edf ph\\u00eda tr\\u00ean (1 gi\\u00e2y). \\n11. \\u1ea4n nh\\u1eb9 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi di chuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1eadm thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng l\\u00ean tr\\u00ean.\\n12. Tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u trong kho\\u1ea3ng 5-7 ph\\u00fat cho m\\u1ed7i b\\u00ean. \\n13. Khi \\u0111\\u00e3 ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh phi\\u00ean \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb, T\\u1eaeT thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef n\\u00fat \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n (n\\u00fat \\u1edf b\\u00ean d\\u01b0\\u1edbi) trong 2 gi\\u00e2y. \\u0110\\u00e8n ch\\u1ec9 th\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd t\\u1eaft. \\n14. Khuy\\u1ebfn c\\u00e1o n\\u00ean b\\u00f4i m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ecf kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m v\\u00e0o v\\u00f9ng da tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u sau m\\u1ed7i phi\\u00ean tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u. \\n15. Sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, v\\u1ec7 sinh \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng th\\u00e9p kh\\u00f4ng g\\u1ec9 c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Opatra Synergy Neck b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n v\\u1ec7 sinh c\\u1ee7a OPATRA ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1eb1ng b\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 tr\\u00f9ng. Lau kh\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u0103n gi\\u1ea5y v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7t l\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ebf.\\n*Ngay sau khi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb, v\\u00f9ng da \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ecf. Trong v\\u00f2ng 1 gi\\u1edd, da s\\u1ebd tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng.\\n\\nV\\u1ec6 SINH THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca\\n\\n\\u2022 Sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, v\\u1ec7 sinh \\u0111\\u1ea7u tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u b\\u1eb1ng th\\u00e9p kh\\u00f4ng g\\u1ec9 c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck Opatra b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n \\u1ea9m (kh\\u00f4ng d\\u00f9ng kh\\u0103n \\u01b0\\u1edbt) ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1eb1ng b\\u00f4ng v\\u00f4 khu\\u1ea9n. Lau kh\\u00f4 b\\u1eb1ng kh\\u0103n kh\\u00f4 m\\u1ec1m ho\\u1eb7c kh\\u0103n gi\\u1ea5y v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1eb7t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb l\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ebf.\\n\\u2022 Lu\\u00f4n lu\\u00f4n v\\u1ec7 sinh thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. \\n\\u2022 Lu\\u00f4n \\u0111\\u1eady n\\u1eafp b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n\\u2022 Tr\\u00e1nh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea9y r\\u1eeda ho\\u1eb7c h\\u00f3a ch\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea9y r\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb. \\n\\nB\\u1ea2O QU\\u1ea2N THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca\\n\\n\\u2022 N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng Synergy Neck trong th\\u1eddi gian d\\u00e0i, T\\u1eaeT thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ea1c v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb \\u1edf n\\u01a1i kh\\u00f4 r\\u00e1o, s\\u1ea1ch s\\u1ebd..\\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck tr\\u00e1nh xa ngu\\u1ed3n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng. \\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea3o qu\\u1ea3n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck tr\\u00e1nh \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng.\\nSYNERGY NECK C\\u1ee6A OPATRA KH\\u00d4NG CH\\u1ed0NG TH\\u1ea4M N\\u01af\\u1edaC\\n\\u2022 KH\\u00d4NG \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc hay c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng kh\\u00e1c \\u0111i v\\u00e0o thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb. \\n\\u2022 KH\\u00d4NG ch\\u1ea1m v\\u00e0o Synergy Neck khi tay \\u01b0\\u1edbt.\\n\\u2022 KH\\u00d4NG \\u0111\\u1eb7t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0o ho\\u1eb7c l\\u00e0m d\\u00ednh n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng kh\\u00e1c v\\u00e0o thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb. \\n\\u2022 KH\\u00d4NG r\\u1eeda thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ho\\u1eb7c c\\u00e1c ch\\u1ea5t l\\u1ecfng kh\\u00e1c. \\n\\nS\\u1ea0C THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca\\n\\n\\u2022 N\\u00ean s\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1ea7y thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 th\\u1eddi gian s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ea1t t\\u1edbi 2 gi\\u1edd khi \\u0111\\u00e3 s\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1ea7y. \\n\\u2022 N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n th\\u1ea5y thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ea1c, h\\u00e3y s\\u1ea1c thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb 2 gi\\u1edd tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n\\u2022 Kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1ea1c qu\\u00e1 2 gi\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u00e1nh l\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb qu\\u00e1 m\\u1ee9c. \\n\\u2022 B\\u1ea1n kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Neck khi \\u0111ang \\u1edf ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ed9 s\\u1ea1c.\"},\"seo_titl\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"SYNERGY NECK\",\"vi\":\"THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca L\\u00c0M \\u0110\\u1eb8P SYNERGY NECK\"},\"gallery_image\":{\"1693453167704\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/5_SYNERGY NECK\\/neck1_1eab33b195f34d8caa826006bacee65a_master.webp\",\"1693453168296\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/5_SYNERGY NECK\\/neck3_fab2a9b44c704b0fbdc78659161571a6_master.webp\",\"1693453168811\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/5_SYNERGY NECK\\/155999529_2757711011163142_2179678887570201392_n_72560e45a024441eba2b376505ba96c0_master.webp\",\"1693453169307\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/opatra london\\/5_SYNERGY NECK\\/70732976_2330385563895691_1985166276854546432_n_7bcc23ec2d664d7196585857ee71d4bb_master.webp\"}}', '/data/cms-image/product/opatra london/5_SYNERGY NECK/neck2_289f3a8ad29a4ddb8157cd3812ba34fb_master.webp', NULL, 0, 9, 5, 'active', 1, 1, '2023-08-16 02:57:48', '2023-09-06 20:02:43', 'synergy-neck');
