(172, 53, 'product', 'SYNERGY MABLE', '{\"price\":\"320000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Opatra Synergy Marble combines LED lights with heating and cooling technology to improve the skin\'s appearance and fight signs of aging, purifying, detoxifying and brightening the skin, helping to reduce fine lines and wrinkles. and tanning, for healthy and youthful skin. For best results, Synergy Marble should be used in combination with Opatra\'s anti-aging skin care line.\",\"vi\":\"Opatra Synergy Marble k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u00e8n LED v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 l\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m l\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i c\\u1ee7a da v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a, l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch, kh\\u1eed \\u0111\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m s\\u00e1ng da, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3m v\\u1ebft nh\\u0103n, n\\u1ebfp g\\u1ea5p da v\\u00e0 s\\u1ea1m da, cho l\\u00e0n da kh\\u1ecfe m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1i tr\\u1ebb. \\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p Synergy Marble v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra.\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Opatra Synergy Marble combines LED lights with heating and cooling technology to improve the skin\'s appearance and fight signs of aging, purifying, detoxifying and brightening the skin, helping to reduce fine lines and wrinkles. and tanning, for healthy and youthful skin. For best results, Synergy Marble should be used in combination with Opatra\'s anti-aging skin care line.\\n\\n\\nINDICATIONS FOR USE\\n\\nThe Synergy Marble device is an over-the-counter device used to: Release energy from red, blue, yellow and infrared light that has a special effect in reducing all pain and helping to heal diseases. wounds, while also helping to improve the appearance and texture of the skin. Clinical studies also show that red, blue, yellow and infrared wavelengths improve the appearance of skin and reduce signs of aging.\\n\\nPHOTOONE THERAPY\\n\\nPhoton therapy is a new therapy that uses the natural healing energy of light to treat inflammation and relieve pain. When light comes into contact with the surface of the skin, it activates the skin\'s light receptors, allowing skin cells to absorb energy from the light. It promotes cellular biochemistry, stimulates collagen production, stimulates cells responsible for pain relief and improves the overall texture and appearance of the skin.\\n\\nBENEFITS OF PHOTON TECHNOLOGY\\n\\nRed LED light - 620-630 nm - Anti-aging\\nRed LED lights help improve skin appearance and fight signs of aging. After use, the skin will be more moist and smooth.\\nUse with Opatra anti-aging cream or serum to increase effectiveness.\\nEliminates\\/reduces signs of aging.\\nHelps improve skin texture.\\nBlue LED light - 460-470 nm - Cleansing - Detoxifying\\nBlue LED light helps improve dark spots and discoloration of skin.\\nUse with Opatra anti-aging cream or serum to increase effectiveness.\\nEffectively soothes the skin.\\nCan help when there are skin problems and when the skin is dark.\\nYellow LED - 589-592 nm \\u2013 Repair \\u2013 Relax\\nYellow LED light hydrates and improves overall skin health.\\nUse with Opatra anti-aging cream or serum to increase effectiveness.\\nSkin looks visibly bright, vibrant and rejuvenated.\\nInfrared \\u2013 850-900 nm\\nRed and infrared (NIR) light can penetrate deeper into the skin than other wavelengths of light. The main property of infrared light is its ability to penetrate deeper layers of the skin, providing significant pain relief.\\nRed light therapy devices that combine both red light and near-infrared light have healing powers because they incorporate a range of therapeutic wavelengths.\\nThese wavelengths can target different tissues. For example, red light wavelengths can penetrate deep into the skin, promoting collagen production and wound healing, while near infrared light can penetrate deeper into body tissues for healing. deeper wounds, treating muscle and joint pain.\\nInfrared light is safe, natural, non-invasive and painless. Therefore, it can bring many health benefits.\",\"vi\":\"Opatra Synergy Marble k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u00e8n LED v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 l\\u00e0m n\\u00f3ng v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m l\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i c\\u1ee7a da v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a, l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch, kh\\u1eed \\u0111\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m s\\u00e1ng da, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3m v\\u1ebft nh\\u0103n, n\\u1ebfp g\\u1ea5p da v\\u00e0 s\\u1ea1m da, cho l\\u00e0n da kh\\u1ecfe m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1i tr\\u1ebb. \\u0110\\u1ec3 thu \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t, n\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p Synergy Marble v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c da ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a c\\u1ee7a Opatra.\\n\\n\\nCH\\u1ec8 \\u0110\\u1ecaNH S\\u1eec D\\u1ee4NG\\n\\nThi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb Synergy Marble l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb kh\\u00f4ng k\\u00ea toa, d\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec3: Gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00f3ng n\\u0103ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1eeb v\\u00f9ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ecf, xanh d\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, v\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t trong l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 m\\u1ecdi c\\u01a1n \\u0111au v\\u00e0 gi\\u00fap ch\\u1eefa l\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi gi\\u00fap c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i v\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft c\\u1ea5u c\\u1ee7a da. C\\u00e1c nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u l\\u