 minutes per area).\\n\\nSubsequent treatments:\\n\\nUse when needed, preferably once a week, for 15-20 minutes each time.\\n\\n**User manual\\n\\nABSOLUTELY DO NOT USE ON THE EYE AREA OR WITH YOUR EYES OPEN! To ensure safe use, the DEVICE operates only when in contact with the skin surface and will automatically shut off when not in contact.\\n\\n*Note that the Perfectio LED infrared device will automatically power off when not in contact with the skin for more than 1 minute.\\n\\nTip: Hold the device tightly, absolutely do not \\\"separate\\\" the EYES from the surface of the skin during use. This will help increase efficiency.\\n\\nUsage Procedure\\n\\nTreatment areas: Face, Forehead and Around the eye area\\n\\n-Step 1: Wash and dry your face. Make sure your face is dry and free of powder, gel or cream.\\n\\n-Step 2: Unplug the DEVICE from the CHARGING BASE. Start the machine, the GREEN LIGHT will flash to signal that the device is operating normally, then the light will light continuously. In case the ERROR LIGHT is on, press the ON\\/OFF power button twice to power off the device and resume operation. If the error light continues to illuminate, contact customer service.\\n\\n-Step 3: Place the CONTACT SURFACE on the area you want to treat. The LED light will work automatically. Gently press and move the DEVICE in a circular motion. The temperature of the Contact Surface will begin to increase slightly. Lift the Perfectio DEVICE away from your skin if it feels too hot. Perform the treatment for 3-5 minutes for each skin area.\\n\\n*CAUTION*: Always keep the device moving on the surface of the skin, holding it for too long may cause skin redness or minor burns. Do not use more often than directed, make sure to follow the process, using too much will cause skin swelling and redness.\\n\\n-Step 4: After completing the treatment, turn off the DEVICE by pressing the ON\\/OFF button. THE OPERATION INDICATOR LIGHT on the DEVICE will turn off.\\n\\n-Step 5: Always remember to apply some moisturizer on the treatment area and gently massage in a circular motion after each use.\\n\\n-Step 6: Clean the device after use, then plug it into the charging dock.\",\"vi\":\"-R\\u1eeda m\\u1eb7t th\\u1eadt s\\u1ea1ch, lau kh\\u00f4 v\\u00e0 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 d\\u00f9ng m\\u1eb7t n\\u1ea1, serum v\\u00e0 kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng\\u2026 \\n\\n-Kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u00e1y khi tr\\u00ean da c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed3 h\\u00f4i, serum, kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ho\\u1eb7c ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch. \\n\\n-S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1eeb 1 \\u2013 3 l\\u1ea7n\\/tu\\u1ea7n trong th\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean, th\\u1eddi gian sau \\u0111\\u00f3 d\\u00f9ng t\\u1eeb 2 \\u2013 3 l\\u1ea7n\\/th\\u00e1ng. \\n\\n-D\\u00f9ng kh\\u0103n kh\\u00f4 ho\\u1eb7c b\\u00f4ng g\\u00f2n lau s\\u1ea1ch b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ea3m \\u1ee9ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00e1y sau khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. \\n\\n-Th\\u1eddi gian s\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1ea7y pin n\\u1eb1m trong kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 30 \\u2013 45 ph\\u00fat. \\n\\n-M\\u1ed9t li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng tr\\u00ean g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t l\\u00e0 5 \\u2013 7 ph\\u00fat, v\\u00f9ng c\\u1ed5 2 \\u2013 4 ph\\u00fat, to\\u00e0n th\\u00e2n t\\u1eeb 7 \\u2013 10 ph\\u00fat. \\n\\n-Tr\\u00e1nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00e1y ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi m\\u1eaft. \\n\\n-Kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng tr\\u00ean m\\u00ed m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c v\\u00f9ng da b\\u1ecb t\\u1ed5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng (tr\\u1ea7y x\\u01b0\\u1edbc, v\\u1ebft b\\u1ecfng, v\\u1ebft th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng\\u2026) . \\n\\n*L\\u00ean k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch cho k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t* \\n\\nHi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a Perfectio s\\u1ebd thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 t\\u1ea7n su\\u1ea5t s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y r\\u00f5 k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 s\\u1edbm h\\u01a1n d\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ebfn. M\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng s\\u1ebd m\\u1ea5t t\\u1eeb 15-20 ph\\u00fat \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n l\\u01b0\\u1edbt nh\\u1eb9 THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca tr\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng v\\u00f9ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb. Trong qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y h\\u01a1i \\u1ea5m \\u0111i s\\u00e2u b\\u00ean trong l\\u00e0n da c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh. \\n\\nLi\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u1ea7u: \\n\\nTrong th\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean (4 tu\\u1ea7n), n\\u00ean s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng 3 l\\u1ea7n\\/tu\\u1ea7n, m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n 15-20 ph\\u00fat (3-5 ph\\u00fat m\\u1ed7i v\\u00f9ng). \\n\\nNh\\u1eefng li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh ti\\u1ebfp theo: \\n\\nS\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng khi c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft, t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n n\\u00ean d\\u00f9ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1eb7n 1 tu\\u1ea7n 1 l\\u1ea7n, m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1eeb 15-20 ph\\u00fat. \\n\\n**H\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\n\\nTUY\\u1ec6T \\u0110\\u1ed0I KH\\u00d4NG S\\u1eec D\\u1ee4NG CHO V\\u00d9NG MI M\\u1eaeT HO\\u1eb6C KHI M\\u1ede M\\u1eaeT! \\u0110\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an to\\u00e0n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca ch\\u1ec9 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng khi ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac v\\u1edbi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da v\\u00e0 s\\u1ebd t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ng\\u1eaft khi kh\\u00f4ng ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac. \\n\\n*L\\u01b0u \\u00fd thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i Perfectio LED s\\u1ebd t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eaft ngu\\u1ed3n khi kh\\u00f4ng ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac da qu\\u00e1 1 ph\\u00fat. \\n\\nM\\u1eb9o nh\\u1ecf: Gi\\u1eef ch\\u1eb7t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb, tuy\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed1i kh\\u00f4ng \\u201ct\\u00e1ch r\\u1eddi\\u201d M\\u1eb6T TI\\u1ebeP X\\u00daC ra kh\\u1ecfi b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da trong su\\u1ed1t qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. Vi\\u1ec7c n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap t\\u0103ng cao hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c. \\n\\nQuy tr\\u00ecnh s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\n\\nKhu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb: M\\u1eb7t, Tr\\u00e1n v\\u00e0 Xung quanh v\\u00f9ng m\\u1eaft \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 1: R\\u1eeda v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m kh\\u00f4 m\\u1eb7t. \\u0110\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o da m\\u1eb7t kh\\u00f4 r\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea5n, gel hay kem. \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 2: R\\u00fat THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca ra kh\\u1ecfi \\u0110\\u1ebe S\\u1ea0C. Kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u00e1y, \\u0110\\u00c8N XANH s\\u1ebd nh\\u00e1y b\\u00e1o hi\\u1ec7u thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u00e8n s\\u1ebd s\\u00e1ng li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c. Trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p \\u0110\\u00c8N B\\u00c1O L\\u1ed6I s\\u00e1ng, b\\u1ea5m n\\u00fat ngu\\u1ed3n ON\\/OFF 2 l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1eaft ngu\\u1ed3n thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i. N\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u00e8n b\\u00e1o l\\u1ed7i v\\u1eabn ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c s\\u00e1ng, li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ed9 ph\\u1eadn CSKH. \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 3: \\u0110\\u1eb7t M\\u1eb6T TI\\u1ebeP X\\u00daC l\\u00ean khu v\\u1ef1c b\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb. \\u0111\\u00e8n LED s\\u1ebd t\\u1ef1 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng. \\u1ea4n nh\\u1eb9 v\\u00e0 di chuy\\u1ec3n THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca theo h\\u00ecnh v\\u00f2ng tr\\u00f2n. Nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 c\\u1ee7a M\\u1eb7t ti\\u1ebfp x\\u00fac s\\u1ebd b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u0103ng nh\\u1eb9. Nh\\u1ea5c THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca Perfectio ra kh\\u1ecfi da n\\u1ebfu c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y qu\\u00e1 n\\u00f3ng. Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eeb 3-5 ph\\u00fat cho m\\u1ed7i v\\u00f9ng da. \\n\\n*CH\\u00da \\u00dd*: Lu\\u00f4n gi\\u1eef thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u00ean b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t da, gi\\u1eef y\\u00ean qu\\u00e1 l\\u00e2u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m \\u1eedng \\u0111\\u1ecf da ho\\u1eb7c b\\u1ecfng nh\\u1eb9. Kh\\u00f4ng s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1edbi t\\u1ea7n su\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o tu\\u00e2n th\\u1ee7 li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u s\\u1ebd khi\\u1ebfn da s\\u01b0ng, t\\u1ea5y \\u0111\\u1ecf. \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 4: Sau khi ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh li\\u1ec7u tr\\u00ecnh, t\\u1eaft THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca b\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u1ea5n n\\u00fat ON\\/OFF. \\u0110\\u00c8N B\\u00c1O HI\\u1ec6U HO\\u1ea0T \\u0110\\u1ed8NG tr\\u00ean THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca s\\u1ebd t\\u1eaft. \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 5: Lu\\u00f4n nh\\u1edb thoa m\\u1ed9t \\u00edt kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m l\\u00ean khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1t xa nh\\u1eb9 theo h\\u00ecnh v\\u00f2ng tr\\u00f2n sau m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng. \\n\\n-B\\u01b0\\u1edbc 6: L\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb sau khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u1eafm v\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ebf s\\u1ea1c.\"},\"seo_titl\":null,\"seo_keyword\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"title\":{\"en\":\"ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE\",\"vi\":\"B\\u1ed8 THI\\u1ebeT B\\u1eca L\\u00c0M \\u0110\\u1eb8P ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE\"},\"gallery_image\":{\"1693450573049\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/zero gravity\\/8_ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE\\/7_silver_blue_treat_set__2__3__916eff9d0a454831b42adabb5f15d078_master.webp\",\"1693450573619\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/zero gravity\\/8_ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE\\/7_silver_blue_treat_set__2__6cb2479818a84696acf071f1f8f2e595_master.webp\",\"1693450574236\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/product\\/zero gravity\\/8_ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE\\/7_silver_blue_treat_set__2__cba789af680e4b9ea0c44529ee73536d_master.webp\"}}', '/data/cms-image/product/zero gravity/8_ZERO GRAVITY- SILVER BLUE/7_silver_blue_treat_set__2__4__6637efdf527c4b55947faa4a23ac1e02_master.webp', NULL, 0