(177, 52, 'product', 'ZERO GRAVITY PERFECTIO X', '{\"price\":\"180000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Wrinkle Prevention | Pain relief | Promotes the production of Collagen, Elastin | Gently erases signs of aging.\",\"vi\":\"Ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n | Gi\\u1ea3m \\u0111au | Th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y s\\u1ea3n sinh Collagen, Elastin | Nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng x\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a.\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Perfectio X is an innovative red and infrared LED light therapy device, designed to deliver incredible anti-aging benefits as well as rejuvenate, firm and strengthen your skin.\\n\\nPerfectio or muscle spasm, increase local blood circulation, relax of muscles.\\n\\nPerfectio X\\u2122 is an FDA Class II medical device. Perfectio x technology gently delivers precise doses to the skin to simultaneously produce collagen and elastin fibers, while erasing signs of aging in all three skin layers. Naturally fills and erases fine lines and wrinkles, lifting and firming skin. LED light therapy is increasingly popular in famous medical spas around the world due to its remarkable effects in reversing signs of aging and various skin imperfections.\\n\\nResults from clinical trials demonstrate both the effectiveness and safety of light therapy in promoting anti-aging skin rejuvenation and increasing collagen in the skin when compared to controls. Research also shows that light therapy is highly effective in reducing pigmentation.\",\"vi\":\"Perfectio X l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng LED \\u0111\\u1ecf v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ea3i ti\\u1ebfn, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch ch\\u1ed1ng l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u00e1ng kinh ng\\u1ea1c c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 l\\u00e0m tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a, l\\u00e0m