(178, 52, 'product', 'ZERO GRAVITY PERFECTIO PLUS', '{\"price\":\"100000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Prevent signs of aging | Improve skin | Evens skin tone | Treat skin problems.\",\"vi\":\"Ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a | C\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0n da | L\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u da | \\u0110i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 tr\\u00ean da.\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"This latest technology can treat signs of aging and wrinkles non-surgically giving you immediate results. It is the only type of treatment approved as a medical device by the FDA.\\n\\nPerfectio+\\/Perfectio is clinically proven and dermatologist recommended.\\n\\nThis device uses LED light with red light and infrared technology. Light penetrates deeper into the skin more effectively than any cream and has been extensively proven by NASA. The device\'s metal tip heats up to 107 degrees F to deliver heat to the treatment area increasing blood flow. An increase in blood flow will provide protein, nutrients and oxygen for better skin repair. LED light promotes the production of cells, collagen fibers as well as elastin tissue, helping the skin become firm and elastic. That way, it rejuvenates the skin. Red light is also known to reduce the amount of melanin in the skin, reducing the appearance of age spots and brown spots. The length of the Perfectio+\\/Perfectio wave can penetrate the skin up to 3mm deep, reaching the dermis, the innermost and thickest layer of the skin.\\n\\nThis therapy device treats all skin layers including the epidermis, dermis and hypodermis, from the surface to the last layer. The advantages of the device include instant results, lifetime warranty, outside-in care with dual action - LED infrared light and heat technology, a powerful combination of treatment and cure at the same time, no side effects, no allergies and it can be used worldwide.\",\"vi\":\"C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb c\\u00e1c d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a v\\u00e0 n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n kh\\u00f4ng nh\\u1edd v\\u00e0o ph\\u1eabu thu\\u1eadt s\\u1ebd cho b\\u1ea1n m\\u1ed9t k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 lo\\u1ea1i h\\u00ecnh \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb duy nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00f4ng nh\\u1eadn nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb y t\\u1ebf b\\u1edfi FDA. \\n\\nPerfectio+\\/Perfectio \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ee9ng minh l\\u00e2m s\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c b\\u00e1c s\\u0129 da li\\u1ec5u khuy\\u00ean d\\u00f9ng. \\n\\nThi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb n\\u00e0y s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng LED v\\u1edbi c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ecf v\\u00e0 tia h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i. \\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng th\\u00e2m nh\\u1eadp s\\u00e2u v\\u00e0o da hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 h\\u01a1n b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 lo\\u1ea1i kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng n\\u00e0o v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ee9ng minh r\\u1ed9ng r\\u00e3i b\\u1edfi NASA. \\u0110\\u1ea7u kim lo\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb s\\u1ebd n\\u00f3ng l\\u00ean t\\u1edbi 107 \\u0111\\u1ed9 F \\u0111\\u1ec3 cung c\\u1ea5p nhi\\u1ec7t t\\u1ea1i khu v\\u1ef1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb l\\u00e0m t\\u0103ng l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u00e1u. S\\u1ef1 gia t\\u0103ng l\\u01b0u l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng m\\u00e1u s\\u1ebd cung c\\u1ea5p protein, ch\\u1ea5t dinh d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v\\u00e0 oxy \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u1ed3i ph\\u1ee5c t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n cho da. \\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng LED th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y s\\u1ea3n sinh t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o, c\\u00e1c s\\u1ee3i collagen c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 m\\u00f4 elastin gi\\u00fap da tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean s\\u0103n ch\\u1eafc v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u00e0n h\\u1ed3i. B\\u1eb1ng c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00f3, n\\u00f3 l\\u00e0m tr\\u1ebb h\\u00f3a l\\u00e0n da. \\u00c1nh s\\u00e1ng \\u0111\\u1ecf c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c bi\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng gi\\u1ea3m l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng melanin trong da, l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed1m \\u0111\\u1ed3i m\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed1m n\\u00e2u. Chi\\u1ec1u d\\u00e0i c\\u1ee7a s\\u00f3ng Perfectio+\\/Perfectio c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 x\\u00e2m nh\\u1eadp s\\u00e2u v\\u00e0o da l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn 3mm, \\u0111\\u1ebfn l\\u1edbp h\\u1ea1 b\\u00ec l\\u00e0 l\\u1edbp trong c\\u00f9ng v\\u00e0 d\\u00e0y nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a da. \\n\\nThi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb tr\\u1ecb li\\u1ec7u n\\u00e0y x\\u1eed l\\u00fd t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c l\\u1edbp da bao g\\u1ed3m l\\u1edbp bi\\u1ec3u b\\u00ec, trung b\\u00ec v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea1 b\\u00ec, t\\u1eeb b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ebfn l\\u1edbp cu\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng. Nh\\u1eefng \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m c\\u1ee7a thi\\u1ebft b\\u1ecb bao g\\u1ed3m \\u0111em l\\u1ea1i k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 t\\u1ee9c th\\u1eddi, b\\u1ea3o h\\u00e0nh tr\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1eddi, ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c t\\u1eeb b\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i v\\u00e0o trong v\\u1edbi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng k\\u00e9p - LED \\u00e1nh s\\u00e1ng h\\u1ed3ng ngo\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 nhi\\u1ec7t, k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd c\\u1ee7a \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 ch\\u1eefa b\\u1ec7nh c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ed9t l\\u00fac, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng ph\\u1ee5, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 d\\u1ecb \\u1ee9ng v\\u00e0 n\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng tr\\u00ean to\\u00e0n th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi.\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"Safety warning information\\n\\nDO NOT USE IN CASE:\\n\\n\\u2022 There are medical conditions that make the skin sensitive to light, such as systemic lupus erythematosus, multiple photodermatosis (PMLE), sun urticaria.\\n\\n\\u2022 History of light-induced convulsions, especially photo-epileptic symptoms, as a single flash of light can trigger a seizure.\\n\\n\\u2022 Currently undergoing chemotherapy and radiation treatment.\\n\\nStop using if skin becomes red for more than 2 days. The cause may be due to sensitivity to light or some other reason. Please contact your doctor for advice.\\n\\nWARNING - to avoid unintended injury:\\n\\nWARNING: DO NOT USE DIRECTLY ON EYES AND EYELIDS.\\n\\nWARNING: DO NOT USE FOR PEOPLE BELOW 18 YEARS old.\\n\\nWARNING: DO NOT USE THE DEVICE IN AREA WITH A HIGH RISK OF CANCER such as DARK BROWN SKIN, BLACK STICKERS ON SKIN, LARGE FREQUENCES, Eczema, Warts. IF NOT FOLLOWING INSTRUCTIONS WILL EFFECT AND LOWER THE EFFICIENCY OF THE TREATMENT.\\n\\nWARNING - TO PREVENT THE RISK OF ELECTRIC SHOCKET THAT MAY CAUSE INJURY OR DEATH:\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not drop or drop the device into water or any other liquid.\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not use Perfectio that is damp or wet.\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not arbitrarily open and repair Perfectio.\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not operate the appliance if the cord or plug is damaged.\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not use the device for purposes other than those described in the user manual.\\n\\nPRECAUTIONS - Follow these precautions to avoid side effects or minor injury and equipment malfunction:\\n\\n\\u2022 Be careful with damaged skin in the treatment area such as sores, psoriasis, eczema, sunburn, herpes, open wounds or rashes. \\u2022 Do not use the device when the skin is infected, burned, or cut because it may cause discomfort or irritation.\\n\\n\\u2022 Do not look directly at the light from the Perfectio DEVICE.\\n\\nPerfectio\'s safety features\\n\\nPerfectio is designed with many safety features in mind:\\n\\nAbsolutely safe for lower temperatures and energy levels.\\n\\nTo protect your skin, a temperature sensor is built into Perfectio.\\n\\nThe sensor ensures that the skin temperature is always within 41\\u00b12\\u00b0C\\/105.8\\u00b135.6\\u00b0F.\\n\\nPerfectio has secure touch.\\n\\nThe DEVICE is built with many safety standards for the eye area. Perfectio\'s light will not be emitted without contact with the skin surface. The full feed switch operates only when the DEVICE Head is in full and depressed contact with the skin.\\n\\nPerfectio has an automatic shutdown mechanism\\n\\nPerfectio\'s LED infrared light has a timer and will automatically turn off completely if it has not been in contact with the skin for more than 1 minute.\\n\\nProtect your Perfectio\\n\\nStore the device in a well-ventilated area free of dust.\\nPerfectio does not tolerate sudden temperature changes.\\nWhen moving from a cold environment (below 10\\u00b0C\\/50\\u00b0F) to a hot environment, only use it after about 3 hours to give the device time to acclimate to the new temperature.\\nThe Perfectio is a dedicated device for home use (as opposed to commercial designs for use in professional environments).\\n\\nPerfectio cleaning\\n\\nAlways clean Perfectio after use\\n\\nWARNING! RISK OF ELECTRIC SHOCK\\n\\nNEVER clean the Perfectio or any part of the device with water or other liquid.\\n\\n1. Unplug the charger from the wall before cleaning.\\n\\n2. Power off the DEVICE by pressing the ON\\/OFF BUTTON.\\n\\n3. Cool the TREATMENT HEAD.\\n\\n4. Wipe the CONTACTED EYES with an alcohol wipe or a cotton swab with alcohol (wet) after each use to prevent the accumulation of grease and keep in a dry place. Storage Store the device and other components in a dry place.\\n\\nWARNING! RISK OF ELECTRIC SHOCK\\n\\nDo not leave the Perfectio device in a place where it is easy to drop or in any place where there is water such as a sink, container, etc.\\n\\nKEEP the power cord Away from high temperatures.\\n\\nZERO GRAVITY WARRANTY PROCESS\\n\\n- Customers who want to claim warranty first need to visit this website: https:\\/\\/www.zerogravityskin.com\\/customer-service\\/warranty-claim\\/\\n\\n**As long as they registered the device on the website within 7 days of purchase.\\n\\nThe process to claim the warranty is as follows