(181, 52, 'product', 'GRANDIO', '{\"price\":\"190000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba v\\u00e0 Gi\\u1ea3m r\\u1ee5ng t\\u00f3c\",\"vi\":\"Ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba v\\u00e0 Gi\\u1ea3m r\\u1ee5ng t\\u00f3c\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Grandio creates three natural effects at once on the treated areas to deliver the fastest, safest, healthiest results for your hair. The technology behind: 1. Mechanics \\u2013 As Grandio rolls over the scalp, thousands of tiny pressures along with vibrations are applied lightly on the scalp. The metal discs massage and instantly increase blood flow to deliver nutrients and oxygen to the skin. This is when the recovery process begins. This process helps the epidermis and dermis to return to its natural state. Skin becomes thicker, stronger, more flexible and healthier. 2. Electricity \\u2013 The discs of the treatment head will roll evenly to deliver microscopic electric currents when in contact with the scalp. This certified design stimulates hair follicles and promotes natural regeneration. 3. Mechanical - Biological - Research shows that zinc and copper delay the action of the hormone DHT. Grandio directly nourishes the scalp with small controlled amounts of zinc and copper. Grandio is effective on all causes of hair loss. It begins with a restorative process and activity to minimize hair loss while supporting your body in regrowing your natural hair. Compare grandio with other treatments on the market today: 4. Drugs - side effects including decreased testosterone levels: Physiological side effects. 5. PRP- (Platelet Rich Plasma) - can cause infection, nerve injury, injection site pain and tissue damage. 6. Laser - the most successful device will only increase the rate of hair growth by 3%. 7. Implant - surgery - invasive and expensive.\",\"vi\":\"Grandio t\\u1ea1o ra ba t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00