(182, 50, 'product', 'ORIGANI ERDA EYE GEL CONCENTRATE', '{\"price\":\"4600000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Ch\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1eafn | Gi\\u1ea3m qu\\u1ea7ng th\\u00e2m | Gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft\",\"vi\":\"Ch\\u1ed1ng nh\\u1eafn | Gi\\u1ea3m qu\\u1ea7ng th\\u00e2m | Gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Erda Eye Gel Concentrate reduces puffiness and dark circles. Eyeseryl\\u00ae peptide reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles while firming the eye contour area. Cucumber Extract reduces puffiness and delivers all-day moisturizing Hyaluronic Acid to the delicate eye area. Your eyes will regain a youthful and fresh look.\\n\\nMAIN INGREDIENT:\\n\\n*Peptide Eyeseryl\\u00ae - tetraPeptide is specially designed high quality to target puffiness and dark circles.\\n\\n*Sodium Hyaluronate (Hyaluronic Acid) - Natural Moisturizing Factor (NMF), has the ability to draw moisture from the air into the skin\'s cells, leaving the outer surface of the skin protected and fully moisturized as well as strengthens and plumps the eye skin.\\n\\n*Kelp (Kelp) - Seaweed is rich in minerals and vitamins to protect the skin from aging caused by the sun. Aloe Vera and Cucumber - Cools, restores and tightens pores.\\n\\nUSES: The main active ingredient ACETYL TETRAPEPTIDE-5 Peptide of Eye Gel Concentrate, helps to reduce puffiness and dark circles, while smoothing fine lines and wrinkles.\",\"vi\":\"Erda Eye Gel Concentrate l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea7ng th\\u00e2m. Peptide Eyeseryl\\u00ae l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi l\\u00e0m s\\u0103n ch\\u1eafc v\\u00f9ng vi\\u1ec1n m\\u1eaft. Chi\\u1ebft xu\\u1ea5t D\\u01b0a Leo l\\u00e0m gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 cung c\\u1ea5p Axit Hyaluronic d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m c\\u1ea3 ng\\u00e0y cho v\\u00f9ng da m\\u1eaft m\\u1ecfng manh. \\u0110\\u00f4i m\\u1eaft c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd l\\u1ea5y l\\u1ea1i v\\u1ebb tr\\u1ebb trung v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1i m\\u1edbi.\\n\\nTH\\u00c0NH PH\\u1ea6N CH\\u00cdNH: \\n\\n*Peptide Eyeseryl\\u00ae - tetraPeptide \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf chuy\\u00ean bi\\u1ec7t ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao \\u0111\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eb1m ti\\u00eau di\\u1ec7t b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea7ng th\\u00e2m. \\n\\n*Sodium Hyaluronate (Axit Hyaluronic) - Y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean (NMF), c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng h\\u00fat \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m t\\u1eeb kh\\u00f4ng kh\\u00ed v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o c\\u1ee7a da, gi\\u00fap b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ngo\\u00e0i c\\u1ee7a da \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 v\\u00e0 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 c\\u1ee7ng c\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m c\\u0103ng m\\u1ecdng da m\\u1eaft. \\n\\n*T\\u1ea3o b\\u1eb9 (Kelp) - Rong bi\\u1ec3n gi\\u00e0u kho\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 vitamin \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 da kh\\u1ecfi qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a do \\u00e1nh n\\u1eafng m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi. Nha \\u0110am v\\u00e0 D\\u01b0a Leo - L\\u00e0m m\\u00e1t, ph\\u1ee5c h\\u1ed3i v\\u00e0 se kh\\u00edt l\\u1ed7 ch\\u00e2n l\\u00f4ng.\\n\\nC\\u00d4NG D\\u1ee4NG: Th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n ho\\u1ea1t ch\\u1ea5t ch\\u00ednh ACETYL TETRAPEPTIDE-5 Peptide c\\u1ee7a Eye Gel Concentrate, gi\\u00fap gi\\u1ea3m b\\u1ecdng m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea7ng th\\u00e2m, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi l\\u00e0m m\\u1edd c\\u00e1c n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 v\\u1ebft ch\\u00e2n chim.\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"*Certified organic ingredients.\\n\\nIngredients: Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice*, Coco-Caprylate, Macrocystis Pyrifera (Kelp) Extract, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Punica Granatum (Pomegranate) Extract*, Macadamia Tern