(189, 50, 'product', 'ORIGANI MANUKA MGO 250+ HONEY PEEL MASK', '{\"price\":\"4000000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Softening | Cleaning | Minimizes wrinkles and evens out skin tone\\n\\nIncludes certified organic ingredients.\\n- Manuka honey MGO 250+ exclusive from Australia.\\nManuka honey exfoliator with gentle antibacterial properties easily removes impurities for radiant skin in just 10 seconds.\\n- It smooths, softens and minimizes the appearance of fine lines, while improving dull skin, fostering a more youthful appearance. Combined with Deer Antler Algae Extract with detoxifying brightening properties, Lotus Extract and Aloe Vera, the skin is boosted with natural moisture, protection and balance.\",\"vi\":\"L\\u00e0m m\\u1ec1m | L\\u00e0m s\\u1ea1ch | Thu nh\\u1ecf c\\u00e1c n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u da\\n\\n- Bao g\\u1ed3m c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ee9ng nh\\u1eadn organic.\\n- M\\u1eadt ong Manuka MGO 250+ \\u0111\\u1ed9c quy\\u1ec1n t\\u1eeb n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u00dac.\\n- T\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft m\\u1eadt ong Manuka v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1eb7c t\\u00ednh kh\\u00e1ng khu\\u1ea9n nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf t\\u1ea1p ch\\u1ea5t cho l\\u00e0n da r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 ch\\u1ec9 sau 10s s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng.\\n- S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m l\\u00e0m m\\u1ecbn, l\\u00e0m m\\u1ec1m v\\u00e0 gi\\u1ea3m thi\\u1ec3u s\\u1ef1 xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a n\\u1ebfp nh\\u0103n, trong khi c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n l\\u00e0n da x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, nu\\u00f4i d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i tr\\u1ebb trung h\\u01a1n. K\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi chi\\u1ebft xu\\u1ea5t t\\u1ea3o g\\u1ea1c h\\u01b0\\u01a1u v\\u1edbi t\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0m s\\u00e1ng da v\\u1edbi gi\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ed9c, chi\\u1ebft xu\\u1ea5t hoa sen v\\u00e0 l\\u00f4 h\\u1ed9i, l\\u00e0n da \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 v\\u00e0 c\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng.\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"MANUKA HONEY EXCELLENT NEW VERSION:\\n\\n1. The Manuka honey scrub now has a new look in a fancy and seductive hexagonal design.\\n\\n2. Manuka honey extract is getting more and more pure and quality with stronger MGO 250+ (old MGO 30). This means the enhanced Manuka honey ingredient has the power to heal and repair the skin, while remaining an effective and gentle exfoliator suitable for most people!\\n\\nSKIN TYPES TO USE MANUKA HONEY PEEL: Rough, dull, uneven skin tone, large pores easily clogged, dehydrated skin\\n\\nCauses of the above skin condition: Damage from UV rays, lifestyle and environment, natural aging, lack of exfoliating steps and inappropriate cosmetic use\\n\\nSkin type: All skin types except very sensitive skin and acne-prone skin\\n\\nWHAT IS SPECIAL WITH THIS PRODUCT? The Manuka Honey Exfoliating Body Scrub is an iconic Australian skin care product that can bring about an immediate change in skin. This product has a multi-effect effect and gently exfoliates the skin of the face. With natural ingredients like Natural Fruit Acids, Aloe Vera and more Manuka Honey MGO 250+, your skin will shine, tone and become more youthful! The skin will be convinced!\",\"vi\":\"T\\u1ea8Y T\\u1ebe B\\u00c0O CH\\u1ebeT M\\u1eacT ONG MANUKA PHI\\u00caN B\\u1ea2N M\\u1edaI C\\u00d3 G\\u00cc M\\u1edaI?\\n\\n1. T\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft m\\u1eadt ong Manuka nay \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 di\\u1ec7n m\\u1ea1o m\\u1edbi trong thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf l\\u1ee5c gi\\u00e1c l\\u1ea1 m\\u1eaft v\\u00e0 quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169.\\n\\n2. Chi\\u1ebft xu\\u1ea5t m\\u1eadt ong Manuka ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 tinh khi\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 MGO 250+ m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd h\\u01a1n (ch\\u1ec9 s\\u1ed1 c\\u0169 MGO 30). \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y c\\u00f3 ngh\\u0129a l\\u00e0 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1eadt ong Manuka \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng s\\u1ee9c m\\u1ea1nh l\\u00e0m l\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 s\\u1eeda ch\\u1eefa l\\u00e0n da, c\\u00f9ng l\\u00fac v\\u1eabn gi\\u1eef nguy\\u00ean ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng t\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi h\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi!\\n\\nLO\\u1ea0I DA N\\u00caN D\\u00d9NG MANUKA HONEY PEEL: Da th\\u00f4 r\\u00e1p, x\\u1ec9n m\\u00e0u, kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u m\\u00e0u, l\\u1ed7 ch\\u00e2n l\\u00f4ng to d\\u1ec5 b\\u1ecb t\\u1eafc ngh\\u1ebdn, da b\\u1ecb thi\\u1ebfu n\\u01b0\\u1edbc\\n\\nNguy\\u00ean nh\\u00e2n g\\u00e2y ra t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng da tr\\u00ean: T\\u00e1c h\\u1ea1i t\\u1eeb tia UV, l\\u1ed1i s\\u1ed1ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, s\\u1ef1 l\\u00e3o h\\u00f3a t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, thi\\u1ebfu b\\u01b0\\u1edbc t\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft v\\u00e0 d\\u00f9ng m\\u1ef9 ph\\u1ea9m kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p\\n\\nLo\\u1ea1i da: T\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 m\\u1ecdi lo\\u1ea1i da tr\\u1eeb da r\\u1ea5t nh\\u1ea1y c\\u1ea3m v\\u00e0 da \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 m\\u1ee5n vi\\u00eam\\n\\nS\\u1ea2N PH\\u1ea8M N\\u00c0Y C\\u00d3 G\\u00cc \\u0110\\u1eb6C BI\\u1ec6T? T\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft m\\u1eadt ong Manuka l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da mang t\\u00ednh bi\\u1ec3u t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb \\u00dac m\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 mang l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ef1 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i l\\u00e0n da ngay l\\u1eadp t\\u1ee9c. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m n\\u00e0y v\\u1eeba mang l\\u1ea1i hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111a t\\u00e1c d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1eeba t\\u1ea9y t\\u1ebf b\\u00e0o ch\\u1ebft nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng cho da m\\u1eb7t. V\\u1edbi th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean nh\\u01b0 Axit tr\\u00e1i c\\u00e2y t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean, Nha \\u0111am v\\u00e0 l\\u01