(231, 50, 'product', 'ORIGANI TOTAL CARE NAIL COLLECTION', '{\"price\":\"2200000\",\"url_link\":\"\\/contact\",\"url_link_title\":{\"en\":\"Contacts Us\",\"vi\":\"Li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 ngay\"},\"brief\":{\"en\":\"Nurturing | Security | Moisturizing\",\"vi\":\"Nu\\u00f4i d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng | B\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 | D\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng \\u1ea9m\"},\"description\":{\"en\":\"Four steps to beautiful, natural nails.\\n\\nThis nail care set provides you all the tools for nail care at home.\\n\\nOrigani Hand & Nail Perfection Cream (100 mL e 3.38 US fl.oz): Provides nutrients and moisture to the skin, making it soft and smooth.\\nOrigani Nourishing Cuticle Oil (10 mL e 0.33 US fl.oz): Nourishes nails\",\"vi\":\"B\\u1ed1n b\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ec3 m\\u00f3ng tay \\u0111\\u1eb9p, t\\u1ef1 nhi\\u00ean. \\n\\nB\\u1ed9 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c m\\u00f3ng tay n\\u00e0y cung c\\u1ea5p cho b\\u1ea1n t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c m\\u00f3ng tay t\\u1ea1i nh\\u00e0.\\n\\nOrigani Hand & Nail Perfection Cream (100 mL e 3.38 US fl.oz): Cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ch\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ea9m cho da, gi\\u00fap da m\\u1ec1m m\\u1ea1i, m\\u1ecbn m\\u00e0ng.\\nOrigani Nourishing Cuticle Oil (10 mL e 0.33 US fl.oz): Cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng ch\\u1ea5t cho ph\\u1ea7n m\\u00f3ng\\n\\n \"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"Ingredient:\\n\\n*Certified organic ingredients\\n\\nNourishing Cuticle Oil (10 mL e 0.33 US fl.oz): Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Rosa Eglanteria (Rosehip) Oil, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Anthemis Nobilis (Chamomile) Flower Oil, Argania Spinosa (Argan) Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E), Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil.\\n\\nHand & Nail Perfection Cream (100 mL e 3.38 US fl.oz): Aqua (Water), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Cetearyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) But