 massage until fully absorbed. Weekly use will help prevent cracking and drying of hands and nails.\\nLuxe Quality Nail File: Gently file nails in one direction until desired shape is achieved.\\nUltra Nail Buffer: Provides a shiny look and stimulates blood circulation to nails, while encouraging healthy nail growth. Multi-functional 3-sided file creates the most perfect natural nail shape and finish.\\nDark Gray Buffer (gray): gently file nails in a single direction to remove ridges and stains. Do not use tips.\\nLight Green Buffer (green): Quickly file nails with back and forth movements to stimulate blood circulation, promoting faster and stronger nails.\\nWhite Buffer (white): Gently polish for a very smooth and luminous look.\",\"vi\":\"Kem d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da tay & m\\u00f3ng - Hand & Nail Perfection Cream(100 mL e 3.38 US fl.oz): thoa l\\u00ean tay v\\u00e0 m\\u00f3ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xuy\\u00ean theo nhu c\\u1ea7u. Nu\\u00f4i d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da tay v\\u00e0 m\\u00f3ng.\\nD\\u1ea7u d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng da tay v\\u00e0 m\\u00f3ng  - Nourishing Cuticle Oil (10 mL e 0.33 US fl.oz): thoa m\\u1ed9t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u1ecf tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea7u ng\\u00f3n tay v\\u00e0 da, m\\u00e1t xa cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi h\\u1ea5p th\\u1ee5 ho\\u00e0n to\\u00e0n. S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng h\\u00e0ng tu\\u1ea7n s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap tr\\u00e1nh n\\u1ee9t v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4 da tay v\\u00e0 m\\u00f3ng.\\nD\\u0169a m\\u00f3ng - Luxe Quality Nail File: Nh\\u1eb9 nh\\u00e0ng d\\u0169a m\\u00f3ng theo m\\u1ed9t h\\u01b0\\u1edbng cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u00ecnh d\\u1ea1ng mong mu\\u1ed1n. \\nD\\u0169a \\u0111\\u00e1nh b\\u00f3ng m\\u00f3ng - Ultra Nail Buffer:  cung c\\u1ea5p v\\u1ebb ngo\\u00e0i \\u00f3ng \\u00e1nh v\\u00e0 k\\u00edch th\\u00edch l\\u01b0u th\\u00f4ng m\\u00e1u cho m\\u00f3ng tay, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch m\\u00f3ng m\\u1ecdc ra kh\\u1ecfe m\\u1ea1nh. 3 m\\u1eb7t d\\u0169a t\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p nh